Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.15,0:00:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,字幕校对+特效: 月亮花@MySiLU思路高清
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.16,0:00:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs48\pos(190.5,206.545)}试金石影业出品
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.15,0:00:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这是地球，\N[Man Narrating] This is the Earth at a time...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.40,0:01:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是恐龙称霸的时代,万物滋长、欣欣向荣\Nwhen the dinosaurs roamed a lush and fertile planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.62,0:01:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,一块只有六英里宽的石头\NA piece of rock just six miles wide...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.21,0:01:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,却改变了这一切\Nchanged all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.97,0:01:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,它以一万枚核弹的威力撞击地球\NIt hit with the force of 10,000 nuclear weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.98,0:01:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,一兆吨的灰尘和沙石 散布在大气层\NA trillion tons of dirt and rock hurtled into the atmosphere,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.57,0:01:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,令人窒息的灰尘掩盖大地\Ncreating a suffocating blanket of dust...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.53,0:01:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,一千年内阳光都无法穿透\Nthe sun was powerless to penetrate for a thousand years.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.67,0:01:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,曾经发生过的…\NIt happened before.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.83,0:01:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,…将会再次发生\NIt will happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.12,0:01:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,主演 : 布鲁斯·威利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.55,0:01:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这是迟早的问题\NIt's just a question of when.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.87,0:02:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(191.7,206.545)}【 世 界 末 日 / 绝 世 天 劫 】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.69,0:02:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(256.5,283.455)}(六千五百万年后)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.99,0:02:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,宇航员，请重复
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.89,0:02:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,请你重覆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.03,0:02:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我收到了，休斯顿\N[Man] Houston, affirmative.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.32,0:02:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我要再试一次\NNow try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,就快好了\NAlmost got it. [Grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,阿特兰蒂斯号，我快好了 休斯顿，彼特的状况不错\NDennis, I'm almost there.  Houston, Pete's lookin' real strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.51,0:02:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,很好，彼特 我们看到联轴器了\NOkay, Pete, we got that coupling on the board here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,等它对准以后 我们就通知你进行操作\NWe'll give you the goahead from down here when it's in alignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,没有问题,给我十秒钟\NSounds good. Give me ten seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.43,0:02:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他的心跳加速\NHis heart rate's racing. Hey, Pete.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,彼特，我是楚门\NIt's Truman.  Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你在上面还好吧，伙计？ 很好\NHow you doing up there, hoss?  Pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.52,0:02:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,彼特，我看到你的生理迹象\NListen, Pete, we got an eye on your meds here. I'll give you a buffalo nickel...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:03:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你能冷静下来 我就送你奖品\Nif you'll calm down just a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你行不行？ 我都听你的\NCan you do that for me?  Whatever you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,很好，我们的时间充裕 你不要急\NOkay, now, we got plenty of time, buddy, so don't you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,进行得很顺利\NLooking good here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,行了\NHe'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,继续吧，阿特兰蒂斯号\NGo ahead, Atlantis.  Roger that, Houston.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,收到，开始把他拉进来\NSuggest we start reeling Pete in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么玩意？\N[Buzzing]  What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\NMy Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,信号中断\NWe're down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,休斯顿！\NHouston!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,完全失去联络\NWe've lost all contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,老史，再放一次\NStewart, play that tape back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.38,0:04:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,休斯顿！\N[Screaming] Houston!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,“五角大厦，太空指挥部”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们受到攻击，受到攻击\NMultiple bogies! Multiple bogies!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,第59区有三…五个不明物体\NSector five, niner. I have three. Now five.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,荧幕都满了\NUnidentified tracks.  My screen's full.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,它们飞向大西洋海岸\NMultiple tracks headed toward the Atlantic seaboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可能遭到导弹突袭\NThis could be a surprise missile attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,总统先生，航天飞机在外太空爆炸\NMr. President, the shuttle Atlantis just exploded in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要三组人!第一组，进行内部检查\NOkay, I want three groups! One: internal malfunction.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,从头到尾彻底检查 也许是机件故障\NGet the log tape. Start working back. Maybe it's a glitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,第二组 请北美空防和太空指挥部\NTwo: I want NORAD, Space Command and the 50th tactical,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,比对每个轨道上的外太空物体\Ncomparing all the space junk you tracked in every orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你们比对以后再比对\NI want you to check, recheck and then do it all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,最后一组，考虑突发状况 设想所有的可能性\NNumber three: wild cards. Anything and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,老罗，快打电话把太空总署的一万一千名人员动员起来\NAll right? Now, Big Ross, get on the telephone. Wake up 11,000 people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.05,0:04:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,让他去,快点\NWalt, get 'em going.  Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,卡尔…卡尔…\NKarl. Karl! Karl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,卡尔\NKarl! Your Stouffer's pot pie's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:04:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你的烤肉馅饼十个钟头前就凉了\Nbeen on the table almost ten hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我要跟你离婚 -妲蒂，发生一件大事\NI want a divorce.  Dottie, I'm on to something big here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.99,0:05:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我不晓得是什么,看来外太空有东西爆炸\NII don't know what this is, but it looks like something's burnin' up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,快去拿我的电话簿 我的电话簿\NGo get my phone book, will you? Get my phone book.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我查太空总署的号码\NGet those names of those guys from NASA.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起，我脸上有写着 我是卡尔的奴隶吗？\NExcuse me! Am I wearing a sign that says, "Karl's Slave"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,快给我去拿电话簿！\NGo get my goddamn phone book!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.33,0:05:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,快去！快去！\NGet the book! Get the book! Get the book!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.43,0:05:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,太空指挥部确认了,没有任何国家发射导弹\NSpace Command is reporting negative. That is zero global launches.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这些可能是坠落地面的航天飞机残骸\NIt might just be a piece of the shuttle breaking up as it comes in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.68,0:05:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,也可能是圣诞老人\NIt might be Santa Claus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,没有获得准确的答案之前，将军\NUntil we get definitive, reliable confirmation, General,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就得进入备战状态\Nwe go to DEFCON Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,* I'm gettin' ready for the big time *
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,* Someday you're gonna say I'm big time too *
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,小狗狗，\NHey, little man! Little Richard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你，咱们要发了\NMe and you, man! We're going to the top, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:06:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,发大财了,我不想一辈子都骑脚踏车\NBig time! I ain't gonna be ridin' this bike for the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗？我要骑摩托车，\NYou know what I'm sayin'? I'm gettin' a motorcycle, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这样才拉风\NWe're gonna travel in style.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,* I'm gettin' ready for the big time *
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.26,0:06:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,* Someday I'm gonna be in big time news *
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你有没有长眼睛？赶着去投胎吗？\NWatch where you're goin'. I bet you, none of you all stop for brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,慢点跑\NSlow down, Little Richard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.19,0:06:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们骑了整个早上 你想要大便么？\NYou've been ridin' all morning. You gotta take a dump?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.78,0:06:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们中断节目\NWe interrupt our regularly scheduled programme...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,为您报导最新消息…\Nto bring you this special report.  Shh, shh, shh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,航天飞机于东部时间凌晨 3点47分在外太空爆炸\NThe shuttle Atlantis exploded in space at 3:47 a.m., Eastern Standard Time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,还给我\NHey! Get, get.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.29,0:06:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我的哥斯拉\NThat's my Godzilla. Come on, now.  Yo, fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.30,0:06:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,胖子，你干嘛欺负我的小狗？\NDon't be kickin' Little Richard. What the hell your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,它在咬我的哥斯拉 你这小黑想怎么样？\NThat dog's eatin' my Godzilla. What's a little runt like you gonna do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,狗狗，去咬他.如果我不是基督徒\NGet him, Richard. Sic him. If I wasn't no Christian,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.06,0:06:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,早就把你这身肥肉拿去榨油了\NI'd be throwin' your fat pineappleeatin' ass through the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么还不走？知道吗？这里是纽约\NWhy we not going?  You know why? 'Cause this is New York City.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,什么怪事都有,搞不好有恐怖份子放炸弹\NAnything could happen. Let's see. Could've been a terrorist bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.95,0:07:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,或是有人被枪杀,今天发薪水\NCould've been a dead body. Somebody shot, stabbed, and it's Friday, payday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,搞不好有人被炒鱿鱼跳楼\NDude, somebody probably didn't get their paycheck. Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.27,0:07:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要去逛街\NI want to go shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想,不过碰到塞车 哪儿也去不了\NMe, too, but we ain't goin' nowhere 'cause this is a traffic jam.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,小狗狗\NLittle Richard!  Right over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我来了，小狗狗\N[Screaming]  Little Richard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.89,0:07:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,撑着点，我来了\NHang on, Little Richard. I'm comin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,别怕\N[Whimpering]  Don't you worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.39,0:07:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我会救你的\NI'm gonna get you outta there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧？撑着点\NYou okay, buddy? Don't worry about it. Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,快打911\NSomebody dial 911!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,屏幕都满了,到处都有\NMy screen's full. They're all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,从芬兰到北美海岸 都有物体冲进大气层\NBogies are breachin' the atmosphere from Finland down the North American seaboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你们看看\NLook at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.89,0:08:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,开战了！\NOh, we at war!  [Screaming Continues]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,萨达姆打过来了！\NSaddam Hussein is bombing us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.87,0:09:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得专心算出它的路线\NLet's stay focused. We need to map the trajectory now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那得花一星期\NThat could take a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,快去做，我要知道 这惨况将结束还是刚开始\NJust find it, okay? I wanna know if the worst is over or if it's on its way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,金将军来电\NWe've got General Kimsey on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,从芬兰到南卡罗莱纳州 都受到攻击\NWe've got hits from Finland to South Carolina.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.13,0:09:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这些不是导弹 到底是什么？\NWe know they're not missiles. Now what the hell is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一场流星雨 它们也把航天飞机击落\NIt's a meteor shower. That's what took out the shuttle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.43,0:09:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,总统马上要知道答案\NI've got the president on Air Force One demanding answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,结束了吗？\N[General] Is it over?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,将军，太空总署有一万一千人在查\NGeneral, we've got 11,000 people at NASA trying to figure that out right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,一有答案就告诉你\NWhen we know, you'll know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.36,0:09:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,卡尔，请仔细说\NOkay, Karl, listen. I want you to take your time. Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.12,0:09:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你绝对是第一个发现它的\NYou're definitely the first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.45,0:09:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,第一个座标是1239…\NOkay, first coordinate. Onetwothreenine. 1239, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:10:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,联邦调查局找到他的位置了,他看到外太空发生爆炸\NF.B.I. locked his location.  Saw an explosion in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\NOkay.  [Whispering]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.63,0:10:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-听着卡尔，这是最高机密 -我当过海军，\NListen, Karl, this is top secret.  Sir, I'm retired Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,懂得保密条例,但是有一件事，\NI know all about classified. But one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,第一个发现它的人 有权利为它命名，对吧？\NThe person that finds her gets to name her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.30,0:10:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\NYes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我要用我老婆的名字命名，妲蒂\NI wanna name her Dottie, after my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,她是个老巫婆 我逃不出她的手掌心\NShe's a vicious lifesuckin' bitch from which there's no escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.73,0:10:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你可真疼老婆 太空搜索组，我是指挥中心主任\NThat's sweet, Karl.  S.D.I., this is flight director!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,马上启动哈伯太空望远镜\NI wanna get that Hubble movin', and I want it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.51,0:10:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,收到\NRoger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.31,0:10:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,启动哈伯望远镜\NWe're movin' the Hubble!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这玩意好大\N[Man] It's enormous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.16,0:10:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这是16时43分的图像\NThis is the anomaly at 1643.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.45,0:10:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这是16时58分的图像\NHere is the anomaly at 1658,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.75,0:10:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这是17时的图像\Nand here is the anomaly at 1700.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.34,0:10:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,别说什么狗屁图像了！\NEnough with this anomaly horseshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-这到底是什么玩意儿？ -一颗陨石\NWhat is this thing?  It's an asteroid, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.43,0:10:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,它有多大？\NHow big are we talking?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.39,0:11:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,估计有九百七十六亿…\NSir, our best estimate is 97.6 billion
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-跟德州面积差不多，总统先生 -是的\NIt's the size of Texas, Mr. President.  YYes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.94,0:11:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们事先一点儿都不知道？\NDan, we didn't see this thing coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,计算星体撞地球的预算只有一百万美元\NWell, our object collision budget's a million dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.15,0:11:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,只能探测百分之三的太空\NThat allows us to track about three percent of the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,恕我直言，太空大得很\NAnd begging your pardon, sir, it's a bigass sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,早上掉下来的呢？\NAnd the ones this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.06,0:11:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,它们微不足道\NThose are nothing. They're the size of basketballs...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.45,0:11:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,只有篮球或甲壳虫汽车那么大而已\Nand Volkswagens, things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.49,0:11:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-这玩意会撞上地球吗？ -我们正在全力计算\NIs this going to hit us?  We're efforting that as we speak, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,-损失会有多大？ -损失？\NWhat kind of damage are we  Damage?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,全面性的损失\NTotal, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.21,0:11:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我们管这叫地球杀手，\NIt's what we call a global killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.76,0:11:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,人类将会灭绝\NThe end of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.97,0:11:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不管它撞上哪里\NDoesn't matter where it hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.26,0:11:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都将被毁灭，包括细菌\NNothing would survive. Not even bacteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天，我们该怎么办？\NMy God. What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.61,0:11:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,在它撞上地球之前，我们只有18天！\NWe have 18 days before it hits Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.52,0:12:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,(南中国海)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.29,0:12:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,早安\N[Man] Have mercy.  Rise and shine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.21,0:12:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,停止钻油…停止钻油…\NStop the drilling! Stop the drilling! Stop the drilling!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.34,0:12:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,球来啦！\NFore!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.01,0:12:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,差一点打到我们\NHey!  Hey, that was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.98,0:12:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我每年都捐出五万元\NI give you 50,000 a year in donations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他们干嘛这么生气，奇克？\NWhat do you think they're so mad about, Chick?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他们认为...\NWell, I think they feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,钻油很邪恶\Nthat drilling for oil is an evil thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.65,0:12:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的船也得用柴油！\NYou know how much diesel that clunker boat pumps out an hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.36,0:12:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,有件事挺有意思,昨晚二号油井钻到180英尺\NI just found out something interesting. Number two chewed 180 feet last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.70,0:12:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这是谁干的？我让你猜猜看\NWho do we have to thank for this?  I'll give you two guesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.29,0:12:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不过你很清楚\NBut you're only gonna need one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.83,0:12:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,该死…小杰\NGoddamn it, A.J.!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.29,0:12:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,小杰\NA.J.!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.21,0:12:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,小杰，你在吗？\NA.J.! A.J., you in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:12:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊，你还在睡觉，起床！\NOh, that's just perfect. In bed. Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.59,0:13:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你找我吗？对，我找你\NUh, hey, you wanted to see me?  Yeah, I was lookin' for ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.72,0:13:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我看得出你在生气\NYou're pissed. Okay, I can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有生气,你见过我生气\NNo. You know what, A.J.? I'm not pissed. You've seen me pissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.77,0:13:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这次我不只是生气\NThis is way, way beyond pissed, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你明知道我昨晚把二号油井关闭了\NYou know I shut down number two last night, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.69,0:13:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-我早有预感 -让我告诉你\NYeah, man, I had a hunch on that.  Let me tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.15,0:13:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,有一天等你长大了\NSomeday, many years from now, when you're all growed up,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.15,0:13:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,拥有自己的钻油公司\Nand you got your own oil company
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.91,0:13:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,和八百万美元的资金\Nand $8 million of your own money on the contract,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.66,0:13:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个笨小子就能 为所欲为、胡搞瞎搞\Nyou can do whatever comes into that  little A.J.idiotin' mind of yours you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不过只要油井上写着我的名字 你就不能违反我的规矩\NBut as long as it says "Harry Stamper Oil" on the rig, you will not disobey my rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.79,0:13:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-明白吗？-我明白了\NYou got that?  Yeah, I do got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.79,0:13:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我要听你说五个字\NAll right, now I need to hear five words from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.59,0:13:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会再犯\N[Together] Never do that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.76,0:13:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我真蠢，我是个白痴 我真不应该，我真笨\NI'm a fool. That was idiotic. II mean, that was stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.30,0:13:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道油井是你的\NI'm an idiot. I know what name's on the sign. I'm not
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.05,0:13:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你是怎么了？\NWhat's goin' on here?  What's goin' on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.93,0:13:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我搞砸了，很紧张\NWell, ll mean, you know, I screwed up. I'm a little edgy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.89,0:13:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-你在我手下多久了？ -很美好的五年\NHow long you work for me?  Five wonderful years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.10,0:13:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这五年来 你从没有这么快认错\NIn five years, you have never apologized to me this quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.77,0:13:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,一定有问题，我要查清楚\NSomething's going on here. I'm gonna find out what it is.  [Stammering]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.86,0:13:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我这次知错能改 我要拿你当榜样\NWell, I'm turning over a new leaf. I'm trying to learn from the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:13:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我要向你看齐\NWhat would Harry do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.87,0:14:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道该怎么说\NI'm at a loss for words.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.25,0:14:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我能解释\NOkay, I can explain this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.83,0:14:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-你能解释吗？ -当然\NYou can explain that?  I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.54,0:14:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我很想听你解释.站着别动\NI would really like an explanation. You just stay right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.55,0:14:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,葛瑞丝？\NGrace?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.80,0:14:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-嗨，哈瑞 -我一直要你叫我老爸\NHi, Harry.  I have asked you repeatedly to call me Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.27,0:14:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉，哈瑞\NSorry, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.35,0:14:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,起来把衣服穿上\NGet up and get your clothes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.69,0:14:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你别走开，我马上回来\NYou just stay right there. I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.37,0:14:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的计划\NHere's what we're gonna do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我要星体撞地球的每一个应变策略\NI want every strategy we've got on nearEarth object collision.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.37,0:14:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,任何想法、计划\NOkay? Any ideas, any programmes,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.40,0:14:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕随手写在餐巾纸上的念头\Nanything you sketched on a pizza box or cocktail napkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.96,0:14:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,三十年来 舆论总在问太空总署是否有必要存在\NFor 30 years, they questioned the need for NASA.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.88,0:15:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,今天就要给他们答案\NToday, we're gonna give 'em the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.76,0:15:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道这事吗，色狼？\NYou know about this, Rockhound?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.09,0:15:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-你早就知道 -不，我一点都不知道\NYou knew?  No, I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.47,0:15:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,哈瑞呢？\NWhere's Harry?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.23,0:15:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,哈瑞，我知道你很生气…\NHarry, whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa. I understand, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.06,0:15:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,谁都会生气\NYou're mad. WhoWho wouldn't be mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.65,0:15:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-他会向你开枪的 -他才不会\NHe's gonna shoot you.  Nah, no, he's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.95,0:15:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,哈瑞，你疯了么？\NHarry!  What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.99,0:15:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,向上帝忏悔吧，小杰\NMake your peace with God, A.J.!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.20,0:15:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他拿着枪，正在向我开枪\NThis guy's got a gun, man. He's shooting at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.37,0:15:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-哈瑞，这可不是开玩笑 -听我说，咱们先谈谈嘛\NHarry, this is not funny!  Harry, listen to me! We can talk this over!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.63,0:15:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-这件事很严重吗？ -很严重\NOh, is this a serious thing?  Yeah, pretty serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.75,0:15:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,大熊，帮帮忙\NBear!  What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.34,0:15:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他在向我开枪 帮我挡一挡\NHe's shootin' at me. You see Harry comin', crack him with that wrench.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.84,0:15:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,小杰的老爸临死前 你答应要好好照雇他的\NYou told A.J.'s dad just before he died that you would take care of the boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.14,0:15:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,向他开枪应该不算照雇他\NNow I'm not sure that shootin' him is takin' care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.30,0:15:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,把枪放下\NWhy don't you put the gun down?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,别插手，大熊，让开\NYou don't want none of this. Get out of my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.64,0:15:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想让他先跑远点\NJust tryin' to give my man a head start, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.89,0:15:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,钻到油之前，你不该杀死你最好的手下\NNot to mention the fact that I don't think you wanna kill the best man on your crew...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.90,0:15:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会杀他的\Nbefore we strike oil.  Aw, Chick, I ain't gonna kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.07,0:16:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我只会打断他的腿 缺条腿照样能干活\NJust gonna take a foot off. A man can work with one foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.24,0:16:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,法兰克缺一只手照样能干活\NYou remember old Frank Marx who worked with one hand all them years?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.03,0:16:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,可是他干的并不好\NYeah, but he wasn't very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.53,0:16:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,把枪放下，你疯了吗\NHarry, put the gun down! You're acting insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.49,0:16:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的，穿好衣服站一边去\NNow, honey, go get some clothes on and get out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.00,0:16:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-你不能控制我的生活 -好吧，去穿衣服，赶紧\N-You can't control my life!  -Fine. Clothes. Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.58,0:16:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手，这可不是闹着玩的\NAll right, stop! All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.61,0:16:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手\NIt was funny for a minute. It's not funny any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.34,0:16:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你这算是违法行为\NFuck!  Harry, this is illegal, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.42,0:16:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是间歇性神经病发作，没有罪\NI'm temporarily insane, Rock. It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.64,0:16:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我像疯子吗？\NDo I look like I'm crazy to you?  Well
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.56,0:16:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,哈瑞，冷静点\NHarry! Hey, just cool down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.77,0:16:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手，住手\NWhat are you doing? Harry, stop! Cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.98,0:16:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说，我很认真,我爱她\NAll right, now, listen. Man to man. I'm serious. I love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.24,0:16:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,答错了\NWay wrong answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.95,0:16:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,哈瑞，别玩真的\NWhoa, whoa, Harry. It's gettin' real.  Harry! Come on, Harry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.83,0:16:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-你打到我了 -你打中他了\NYou shot me!  You shot him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,根本就没打中 只是擦伤而已\NThat bullet never got close. Just a ricochet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.62,0:16:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,有人受伤就不好玩了\NYou know, it's all funny till somebody gets shot in the leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.08,0:17:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计们，打起精神来 客户来啦\NHey, pucker up. We got clients incoming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.34,0:17:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在…1974年…\NUh, bback inin in 1974,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.51,0:17:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就…想到…有…陨石…\Nwewe first got the idea
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.68,0:17:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,撞地球的…可能\Nthethe possibility thatthat a meteor or an asteroid
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.10,0:17:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,要找个不结巴的人来讲 博士，翻译给我听\NI need somebody who's had a little less caffeine this morning. Doc, translate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.72,0:17:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,第一个方案是 用散焦激光\NYes, sir. Our first feasibility plan was to use a spreadfocus laser generator...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.85,0:17:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,把陨石击碎\Nto heat the object to the point of fracture.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.90,0:17:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那就像对着火车头开玩具枪\NThat's like shooting a B.B. gun at a freight train, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.28,0:17:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有一个点子\NUh, some of us have got this idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.28,0:17:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,派航天飞机在陨石上架风帆\NWe wanna land a craft, deploy solar sails.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.91,0:17:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,利用这块大风帆 借着太阳风推动陨石\NYou'll have a big canopy. Solar winds will be caught by these Mylar sails.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.58,0:17:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计们，\NOkay  Come on, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.46,0:17:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,实际一点好吗？ 只剩下十八天了\NWe gotta come up with something realistic here. We got 18 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那是431小时15分18秒\NThat's 431 hours, 15 minutes and 18 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.09,0:17:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们没有时间了 -干嘛？\NTime's a luxury we don't have. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.35,0:17:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,小杰是我的选择\NListen, Harry, A.J. is my choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.81,0:17:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不是你的\NMy choice and not yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.06,0:17:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这里只有他的年纪跟你差不多\NHe's the only one in your age bracket, Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.35,0:17:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你是别无选择\NIt's not a choice. It's a lack of options.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.35,0:17:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你凭什么觉得\NI don't know what in the world makes you think...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.81,0:18:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你还能控制我的生活？\Nthat you have the right to tell me what to do any more, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.65,0:18:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,就凭我是你老爸，这还不够吗？\NI suppose being your father doesn't count, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.65,0:18:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-那不是理由 -从几时开始的？\NNot really.  Since when?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.32,0:18:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,从我十岁时比你更成熟时开始\NSince I reached the age of ten and became older than you, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.91,0:18:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,或者从妈妈离开以后 两个“开始”随你选\NSince Mom split. Why don't you take your pick?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.91,0:18:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你天生就很不成熟\NLook, I understand that you  are handicapped by natural immaturity,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.37,0:18:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我原谅你\Nand I forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.42,0:18:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,就算我当老爸不成熟 可我还是你的老板\NI may be an immature father, but I'm still your employer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.67,0:18:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你马上坐船离开\NAnd as your boss, I want you on that crew boat tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.73,0:18:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,礼拜一就回办公室\Nand back in the office by Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.96,0:18:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-听懂了吗？ -好吧，我不干了！\NYou got that?  Okay. I quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.18,0:18:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能不干\NGrace, you can't quit now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.05,0:18:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我还需要你帮忙\NI need you to keep on working.  [Speaking Chinese Dialect]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.60,0:18:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨，哈瑞\NHi, Harry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.35,0:18:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你在笑什么？\NWhat are you smilin' about?  [Speaking Chinese Dialect]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.65,0:18:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我和小杰约会有五个月了\NI've been seein' A.J. for more than five months, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.23,0:18:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,请跟我来\N[Speaking Chinese Dialect]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.24,0:18:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你真没良心 我以前有管过你吗？\NYou little hypocrite. I ever held you back once from doing anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.86,0:18:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你是没有管过我\NWhat about having a life, Harry?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.86,0:18:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我第一次来月经时\NThe first time I got my period,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.35,0:18:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是色狼带我到台北买卫生棉\NRockhound had to take me into Taipei for Tampax...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.83,0:18:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他还教我怎么用\Nand then he had to show me how to use 'em, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.00,0:19:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是跟她解释 没有亲自示范给她看啊\NI ju No, ll told her how to use it. I didn't show her, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.34,0:19:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我的玩具不是洋娃娃 而是钛合金深度仪表\NI was playing with titanium depth gauges when I should've been playing with dolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.34,0:19:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我从费弟的刺青上知道男女之间那事儿\NI mean, I learned about the birds and the bees from Freddie Noonan's tattoos.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.68,0:19:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我被一群钻井工养大\NLook, I was raised on roughnecks by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.47,0:19:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,当我爱上这种人，你却大惊小怪\NAnd now you get all shocked and shaken when I fall in love with one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.14,0:19:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你说谁才没有良心？\NSo who's the hypocrite here, Harry, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.07,0:19:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,请看看那些油管多棒\NLook at those nice pipes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.31,0:19:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-听我说… -你听我说，我长大了\NListen to me, Grace.  No, you listen to me, Harry. I grew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.19,0:19:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,陨石太接近地球 时间所剩不多\NWith the proximity of the asteroid and no prep time,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.45,0:19:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,任何防范措施都没用\Nnone of our primary plans can work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.78,0:19:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,为何不用150枚核弹把它炸成碎片？\NWhy don't we just send up 150 nuclear warheads and blast that rock apart?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.37,0:19:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,烂点子\NTerrible idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我在问你吗？\NWas I talkin' to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.58,0:19:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这是研究部的昆西博士\NThis is Dr. Ronald Quincy from Research.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.46,0:19:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,地球上最聪明的人,你最好听听他的意见\NPretty much the smartest man on the planet. You might wanna listen to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.38,0:19:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,若是考虑陨石的\NGeneral, if you consider your target,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.05,0:19:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,成分、大小…\Nher composition, her dimensions,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,和绝对速度\Nher sheer velocity,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.55,0:19:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,就算发射再多的核弹\Nyou could fire every nuke you've got on her,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.15,0:19:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,它还是照样会撞上地球\Nshe'll just smile at you and keep on coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.60,0:19:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,总统的科学雇问认为\NYou should know that the president's scientific advisors...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.68,0:20:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,发射核弹能使它改变轨道\Nare suggesting that a nuclear blast could change this asteroid's trajectory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.60,0:20:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我认识总统的科学雇问 我们在麻省理工是同学\NI know the president's chief scientific advisor. We were at M.I.T. together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.36,0:20:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,碰到这种情况\NAnd, in a situation like this, [Clears Throat]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.74,0:20:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,最好别听一个天体物理只拿C-的学生\Nyou really don't wanna take the advice from a man who got a Cminus in astrophysics.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.03,0:20:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,总统的科学雇问错了,我才是对的\NThe president's advisors are wrong. I'm right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.33,0:20:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,爆破陨石的表面 一点用都没有\NHitting the rock from the outside won't do the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.12,0:20:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,想想看，把鞭炮放在掌心\NImagine a firecracker in the palm of your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.46,0:20:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,然后点燃，会怎样？只会灼伤手掌\NYou set it off. What happens? Burn your hand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.01,0:20:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,若是用手掌握住鞭炮再点燃…\NYou close your fist around the same firecracker and set it off
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.30,0:20:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你以后连开罐头都要老婆代劳了\Npoof your wife's gonna be opening your ketchup bottles the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.64,0:20:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说我们应该从陨石内部爆破？\NAre you suggesting that we blow this thing up from the inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.23,0:20:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-没错 -怎么做？\NThat's exactly what I'm saying.  How?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.27,0:20:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,钻洞\N[Sighs] We drill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.81,0:20:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,找全世界最顶尖的钻洞专家\NWe bring in the world's best deepcore driller.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.02,0:20:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,快上来，出问题了\NHarry, get up here. We're takin' a hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.07,0:20:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,叫小杰上来\NGet A.J. up here!  Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.70,0:20:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,把油管抽出来，快点\NSend another pipe down! Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.03,0:20:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,钻到天然气了\N[Yelling Continues]  It's a gas pocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.12,0:20:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我就说吧，我是个天才\NI told you! Am I lucky, or am I just a genius?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.50,0:21:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,放油阀坏了我才关闭油井的！\NI shut it down for a reason, you jackass! The relief valve's
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.50,0:21:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,关掉二号阀.葛瑞丝，快把客户带走\NShut off the number two valve! Grace, get the clients out of here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.64,0:21:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,奇克，快把他们带走\NChick, get 'em outta here! Get 'em off the rig now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.40,0:21:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,快跑\NGet the hell down!  This thing is gonna blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.36,0:21:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,快点下来\N[Yelling Continues]  Chick, get down now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.49,0:21:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,奇克，快下来\NGet down!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.75,0:21:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我们打听过很多人 他们都推荐同一个人\N[Dan] Three dozen research calls, and every time, the same man is recommended.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.88,0:21:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他熟悉地球上所有的地形\NHe's worked on every terrain this planet can offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.30,0:21:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,最不可能钻洞的地质他都钻得进去\NWhenever they said it couldn't be drilled, this guy drilled it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.22,0:21:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-大伙没事吧？ -我们钻到石油了\NEverybody all right?  We struck oil, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.38,0:21:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才差点搞出人命 要这样你才甘心吗\NSomebody could've got killed out here today. You want that on your conscience?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.52,0:22:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,干得好，你太棒了\NHigh thumb. You are man, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.56,0:22:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThumbs high.  [Helicopter Blades Whirring]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.94,0:22:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你被解雇了\NYou're fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.86,0:22:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,哪位是哈瑞·史坦普？\NWho's Harry Stamper?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.49,0:22:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是哈瑞·史坦普 有什么事？\NHey, I'm Harry Stamper. What's all this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.79,0:22:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我是孟将军 太平洋空军总司令\NMr. Stamper, I'm General Montgomery, commander of the Pacific air forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.04,0:22:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,国防部长奉总统的命令\NI've been sent here by the secretary of defense...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.88,0:22:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,派我来这里找你\Non direct orders from the president of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.59,0:22:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,事关国家安全\N[Chuckling]  It's a matter of urgent national security.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.84,0:22:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,请你马上登上直升机 不要多问\NI need you to get on that chopper right now, no questions asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.09,0:22:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,疯子威利叫你来的吗？\NCrazy Willie put you up to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.22,0:22:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我不认识疯子威利,我是认真的\NI'm afraid I don't know Crazy Willie, sir. I'm dead serious about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.98,0:22:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,哈瑞.怎么了？\NHarry.  What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.52,0:22:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我发誓我不知道她未成年\NI swear to God, she never told me her age.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.56,0:22:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,别紧张，他是来找我\NIt's all right. Relax. It's about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.98,0:22:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,算我没说\NOh. Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.41,0:23:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，我去,不过我有个条件\NAll right, General, I'll go with you on one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.79,0:23:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我要带我女儿一起去\NWe're gonna have to take my daughter along.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.17,0:23:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我做了什么？\NWhat did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.80,0:23:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\NWhoa, whoa, whoa. Where you guys takin' her?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.67,0:23:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,先生，请呆在这儿\NSir, stay right here.  Wh
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.00,0:23:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,奇克，叫他们领了工资就放假\NChick, get him paid, get him off the rig!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.70,0:23:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,(休斯顿，太空总署)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.98,0:23:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,哈瑞·史坦普先生吗？\NMr. Stamper?  Yeah, I'm Harry Stamper.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.48,0:23:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\NHow you doin'? Miss Stamper.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.90,0:23:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,史坦普小姐 我是丹楚门，太空总署署长\NI'm Dan Truman, Executive Director here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.90,0:23:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我要代表大家向你们…\NListen, on behalf of all of us, I'd really like to apologize
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.56,0:23:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,别向我们道歉\NApologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.24,0:23:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们受够了\NI don't know if we can take any more apologies, Mr. Truman.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.66,0:23:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这十八个小时来 一直有人在道歉\NWe've been apologized to for the last 18andahalf hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.28,0:23:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么话就请直说吧\NSo if you don't mind, how about if we just get on with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.41,0:23:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么把我们找来太空总署\NYou tell us why we're here at the NASA Space Center.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.37,0:23:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们最好单独谈\NWe should probably talk alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.62,0:23:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都跟我女儿葛瑞丝说\NMr. Truman, I don't keep any secrets from my daughter, Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.29,0:23:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,要么你直接说\NSo whether you tell her now or I tell her later,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.17,0:23:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,要么一会我告诉她\Nshe's gonna find out one way or the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.80,0:23:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你还是快说吧\NSo why don't we just get on with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.80,0:23:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这颗慧星撞上陨石带 它的碎片冲向地球\N[Dan] So when the Rogue comet hit the asteroid belt, it sent shrapnel right for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.80,0:24:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,未来十五天内 地球就像个练靶场\NFor the next 15 days, the Earth's in a shooting gallery.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.14,0:24:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,就算陨石本身撞进大海 还是会波及陆地\NEven if the asteroid itself hits the water, it's still hitting land.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.10,0:24:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,它会使海水沸腾 然后直接撞进海底\NIt'll flash boil millions of gallons of seawater and slam into the ocean bedrock.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.98,0:24:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,比如说它撞进太平洋\NNow, if it's a Pacific Ocean impact which we think it will be
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.40,0:24:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,会造成三英里高的海啸\Nit'll create a tidal wave three miles high,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.32,0:24:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,以一千英里的时速淹没加州 一直席卷到丹佛\Ntravelling at 1,000 miles an hour covering California and washing up in Denver.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.03,0:24:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,日本会直接消失，澳洲也会被淹没\NJapan's gone. Australia's wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.70,0:24:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,全球有一半人口将被高温烧死\NHalf the world's population will be incinerated by the heat blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.38,0:24:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,另一半则被严寒冻死\NThe rest'll freeze to death from nuclear winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.63,0:24:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,真不敢相信！\N[Whispering] That's unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.46,0:24:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这是千真万确的\NWell, actually, this is as real as it gets.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.89,0:24:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,它正撞向地球\NWell, it's coming right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.43,0:24:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,以两万两千英里的时速\NRight for us at 22,000 miles an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.73,0:24:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,地球上谁也逃不掉\NNot a soul on Earth can hide from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.78,0:25:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,“15天零3小时”
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.20,0:25:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你们还没正式公布吧\NI take it you're not alerting everyone like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.00,0:25:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不打算把这消息公开\NNobody knows. That's the way it stays.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.88,0:25:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,未来十天内只有九座望远镜看得到这陨石\NFor the next ten days, there are only nine telescopes in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.34,0:25:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,美国就有八座\Nthat can spot the asteroid, and we control eight of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.67,0:25:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,总统把这件事列为最高机密\NThe president's classified this information top secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.76,0:25:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,要是把这消息公诸于世\NIf news like this got out,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.72,0:25:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,全球的社会秩序就会崩溃\Nthere'd be an overnight breakdown of basic social services worldwide.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.14,0:25:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,造成暴动、宗教狂热,全面的混乱\NRioting, mass religious hysteria, total chaos, you can imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.56,0:25:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,就像圣经记载的世界末日\NBasically the worst parts of the Bible.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.11,0:25:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,全球有六十亿人\NSix billion people on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.53,0:25:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你们为什么会找上我呢？\NWhy'd you guys call me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.91,0:25:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要你训练上去的队员\NWe need you to prep the team we're sending up.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.16,0:25:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,上去？\NUp?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.41,0:25:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他们要到陨石表面 钻一个洞放置核弹\NWe'll send them to the asteroid, they'll land, drill a hole, they'll drop some nukes,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.00,0:25:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,离开后引爆，不过器材有些问题\Ntake off and detonate, if we can fix this equipment problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.08,0:25:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这是为火星计划打造的钻头\NThe drilling unit's a prototype we've been building for the Mars project.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.05,0:25:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你…你应该认得\NYou, uh You might recognize the rig.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.01,0:26:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然认得出,这是我设计的\NYeah, well, I guess I should recognize it. It's my design.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.02,0:26:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你们偷走我的专利？\NDid you steal a key to the Patent Office?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.67,0:26:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,基本上可以这样说\NYeah, basically.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.77,0:26:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,让我搞清楚先\NLet me get this straight. I got pulled off an oil rig,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.69,0:26:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我绕了半个地球跑来这里 却发现你们偷走我的专利\Nflown halfway around the world because you stole my drill design.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.86,0:26:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,而且没有看懂图纸，做得烂透了\NCouldn't read the plans right and did a pisspoor job of putting it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.95,0:26:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-在外太空没有专利权… -闭嘴，昆西\NPatents don't apply to outer space.  [Dan] You shut up, Quincy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.53,0:26:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,钻头不再用于火星项目 现在只有它能拯救地球\NIt's not going to Mars any more. It's gonna try to save this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.04,0:26:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你得帮我们搞定它\NAnd we need to know what's wrong with it pretty quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.37,0:26:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说我们没做好钻头？\NYou said we did a bad job of putting it together?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.45,0:26:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不,我是说...\NNo, I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.63,0:26:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说你们做得烂透了！\Nyou did a pisspoor job of putting it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.05,0:26:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,首先，传送系统弄反了,让我猜猜\NFirst of all, you got the flow system all reversed. Let me guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.47,0:26:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你们把叶轮拆开却搞不懂怎么用\NYou've been tearin' up rotors and you can't figure out why.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.86,0:26:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.18,0:26:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因为凸轮装错了，天才\NWell, that's because your cams are all wrong, Mr. Wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.85,0:26:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,谁负责操作这玩意？\NWho's been operating this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.18,0:26:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他们\NRight there.  We've actually
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.60,0:26:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们让他们训练了八个月\NWe've had them training for eight months solid now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.96,0:26:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,整整八个月吗？\NEight whole months?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.27,0:26:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-差不多 -真服了\NWell, pretty much, yeah.  Well, gee whiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.86,0:26:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这就上陨石的钻洞小组\NWell, this is the team that has to do the job up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.32,0:27:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,请你在这里训练他们\NWe need you to train them down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.41,0:27:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,史坦普先生，怎么样？\NWell, Mr. Stamper, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.24,0:27:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,钻洞是门科学也是门艺术\NYou know, drilling's a science. It's an art.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.54,0:27:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我是第三代钻井工 我一辈子都干这行\NI'm a third generation driller, doin' it all my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.79,0:27:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,还是没有完全搞懂\NI still haven't got it all figured out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.12,0:27:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜你是听说我最行 才会把我找来\NI assume you sent for me because somebody told you I was the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.50,0:27:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因为我有最好的工人\NWell, I'm only the best because I work with the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.46,0:27:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,如果没有值得信任的工人 你就死定了\NYou don't trust the men you're working with, you're as good as dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.47,0:27:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你尽管派他们去吧\NNow you wanna send these boys into space, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.72,0:27:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是很好的宇航员\NI'm sure they'll make good astronauts,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.72,0:27:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,可是他们对钻洞一窍不通\Nbut they don't know jack about drillin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.52,0:27:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-你有什么应变措施？ -应变措施？\N-What's your contingency plan?  -Contingency plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.35,0:27:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,备用计划 一定有备用计划吧\NYour backup plan. You gotta have some kind of backup plan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.60,0:27:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,没有备用计划，\NNo, we don't have a backup plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.65,0:27:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,只有这一个\NThis is it.  This is the best that you could
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.65,0:27:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,美国政府就只能想出这个办法吗？\Nthat the government the U.S. government can come up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.11,0:27:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这可是太空总署 你们把宇航员送上月球\NI mean, you're NASA for cryin' out loud. You put a man on the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.49,0:27:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你们都是天才，聪明得不得了\NYou're geniuses. You're the guys that think this shit up.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.87,0:27:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,一定有一大堆人在想办法\NI'm sure you got a team of men sittin' around somewhere right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.45,0:27:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,还有人在想备用计划\Njust thinkin' shit up and somebody backin' them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.92,0:27:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说没有备用计划？\NYou tell me you don't have a backup plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.36,0:27:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这八个人\Nthat these eight Boy Scouts right here,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.71,0:27:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,就是全世界的救星？\Nthat is the world's hope, that's what you're tellin' me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.02,0:28:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.26,0:28:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,老天，该死\NOh, Jesus. Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.01,0:28:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们剩下的时间不多了 你能帮忙吗？\NWe're a little short on time here. Will you help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.85,0:28:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-他们只要钻洞？ -没错\NAll they gotta do is drill?  That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.06,0:28:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不必太空行走，做什么高难度动作？\NNo spacewalkin', no crazy astronaut stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.29,0:28:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,只要钻洞\NJust drill.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.57,0:28:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算要派多少人上去？\NHow many men were you plannin' on takin' up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.57,0:28:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,两艘航天飞机，两组人员\NWe're sendin' up two shuttles, two teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.74,0:28:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我要用我的手下\NIf I do this, I'm gonna wanna take my own men.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.16,0:28:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题\NYou got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.79,0:28:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,-你愿意帮忙吗？ -愿意\NSo you're saying you'll help us?  Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.87,0:28:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.72,0:28:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是不相信别人\NI just don't trust anybody else to do it, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.05,0:28:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不是，寇太太，\N[Siren Wailing]  No, Mrs. Curlene.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.43,0:28:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我是哈瑞·史坦普, 你看到大熊就说哈瑞在找他\NIt's Harry Stamper. You see Bear, you tell him Harry's lookin' for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.23,0:28:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他们下了油井就乱跑\NThose guys get off this rig, they scatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.90,0:28:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,寇家强，绰号大熊\NJ. Otis Curlene Bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.90,0:29:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,南达科塔州唯一的黑人骑士\NProbably the only black man on a big hog in Kadoka, South Dakota.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.69,0:29:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,来抓大熊呀\NCome and get Papa Bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.78,0:29:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,麦斯,外太空有没有体重限制？\NUh, Max.  You got a weight limit on the shuttle?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.62,0:29:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,老妈\NMax.  Hey, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.37,0:29:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你真乖\NSo sweet, Maxie.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.54,0:29:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你有没有买果酱甜甜圈？\NHey, would you give me one of them yellow jelly bear claws I like?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.00,0:29:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-又惹麻烦了吗？ -才没有\N-Are you in trouble with the law again?  -No, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.88,0:29:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-麦斯 -我发誓，妈妈\NMaxie.  I swear, Mama. I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.64,0:29:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我要色狼\NYou know I want Rockhound.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.49,0:29:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他很色，所以…绰号是色狼\NWe call him Hound because, well, he's horny.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.10,0:29:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,到新奥尔良的每一家酒吧 应该能找到他\N[Grace] You might wanna start with every bar in New Orleans.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.02,0:29:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这颗钻戒很大吧？\NThat is a big, shiny mount, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.69,0:29:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,-你结婚多久了？ -两个礼拜\NHow long you been married?  For two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.07,0:29:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,-你看到吗？ -看到\NSee this diamond?  Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.86,0:29:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是钻石\NIt's not a diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.79,0:29:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-想再喝一杯吗？ -好\NWould you like another drink?  Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.74,0:29:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,先生，联邦调查局\NSir, F.B.I.  So cute. No, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.70,0:29:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-事关国家安全 -那敢情好\NWe have a national security matter.  Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.50,0:29:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,马上跟我走\NLet's go. Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.17,0:29:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底几岁？\NHow old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.17,0:30:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,怪怪的奥斯卡 优秀的地质学家\NOscar Choice. Spacy but absolutely brilliant geologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.76,0:30:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他在德州有座农场\NHe owns a horse ranch outside of El Paso.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.76,0:30:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,奇克查普先生\NMr. Chick Chapel, at the craps table.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.98,0:30:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他一定是在赌城的凯撒皇宫掷骰子\NCaesar's Palace, Las Vegas, Nevada.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.23,0:30:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,终于赢了\NYes! About time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.11,0:30:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,奇克·查普？别玩了\NCharles Chapel, game's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.36,0:30:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,要谁操作另一个钻头？ 班尼如何？他不错\NWho's gonna run the other rig? How about Benny? He's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.95,0:30:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该知道小杰是不二人选\NThe only one who knows how to run it as well as I do is A.J.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.24,0:30:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你说他不值得信任\NI thought you said you couldn't trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.71,0:30:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你说他值得信任\NI thought you said I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.71,0:30:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你也独当一面了，小杰\NYep, you are on your way, A.J.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.71,0:30:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,自己当老板有很多好处\NWell, being in business for yourself has its advantages.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.55,0:30:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不必打卡上班 没有人会开枪射我\NMake my own hours, nobody shoots me in the leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.80,0:30:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你没带枪吧？\NYou don't got a gun on you now, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.97,0:30:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好\NOh, good, 'cause I kinda wanted to get back to this whole thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.27,0:30:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们再谈谈 你为什么找我帮忙\Nabout you askin' me for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.90,0:31:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,难道无所不能的\NDoes that mean that there's a job...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.73,0:31:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,万事通哈瑞·史坦普\Nthat Mr. AllGoNoQuitBigNuts Harry Stamper...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.32,0:31:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,也有搞不定的事？ 需要用到我的特长吗？\Ncan't handle by himself and needs my expert advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.32,0:31:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,算是吧\NSomethin' like that, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.03,0:31:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这可不行，\NWell, no, no, no, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.03,0:31:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你说算是 到底是不是呢？\NI mean, is it something like that, or is it that?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.41,0:31:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们真的合不来\NYou know, you and me got a real problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.50,0:31:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,哈瑞，现在我只想听你\NYou know, Harry, there are only...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.42,0:31:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,说出五个字\Nfive words I wanna hear from you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.88,0:31:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是\NThose words are:
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.76,0:31:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,小杰，我佩服你\NYou know, A.J., I really look up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.18,0:31:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我的偶像\NYou've been a hero of mine for a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.38,0:31:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我好崇拜你，\Nand I'm very impressed with your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.26,0:31:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,只是不好意思说\NI'm emotionally closed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.63,0:31:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那好像不只五个字\NThat's like That's like 11 words or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.14,0:31:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那就说，小杰，对不起\NYou know what? How about just, "A.J., I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.06,0:31:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你\Nand I love ya."  You know, A.J.,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.48,0:31:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,小杰，在地球上，我永远都不想再跟你共事\Nthere's not a job on the planet I want you to work with me on.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.91,0:31:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说真的\NI mean that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.74,0:31:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那你为什么要来？哈瑞，到底什么事？\NSo what are you doin' here? Harry, what's the job?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.04,0:32:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,麦斯，好兄弟\NHey, Bear.What's up, baby? Yeah, baby. What's up? What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.88,0:32:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么是太空总署？ 在天王星找到石油了吗？\NWhat's up, Harry? Did NASA find oil on Uranus, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.02,0:32:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以不去,我们大可坐在这里，\N[Harry] None of you have to go. We can just sit here on Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.98,0:32:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,等这块大石头撞上来\Nwait for this big rock to crash into it...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.90,0:32:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,摧毁地球上的一切\Nand kill everything and everybody we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.07,0:32:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,美国政府要我们拯救世界\NThe United States government just asked us to save the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.24,0:32:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-谁打算拒绝？ -二十年来\NAnybody wanna say no?  Twenty years.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.99,0:32:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没拒绝过你 现在也不会\NHaven't turned you down once. I'm not about to start now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.58,0:32:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我参加\NI'm there.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.84,0:32:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能一个人去\NGuess I can't let you go up there alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.86,0:32:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你去\NI'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.05,0:32:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这是历史性壮举\NI mean, this is this is historic.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.38,0:32:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是超级英雄\NGuys, this is like deep blue hero stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.39,0:32:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然参加\NOf course I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.43,0:33:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然我没他那么兴奋 不过你也知道\NWhile I don't share his enthusiasm, you know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.44,0:33:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,送我上去吧\NBeam me up, Scotty.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.06,0:33:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-你呢，麦斯？ -我不知道…\N-You all right, Max?  -I..I don't I..I don't
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.49,0:33:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你说去就去\NWhatever you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.86,0:33:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-你呢？ -我去\N-What about you?  -I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.45,0:33:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NAll right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.62,0:33:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一起去\NWe go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.62,0:33:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是斤斤计较，不过…\NI don't mean to be the materialistic weasel of this group,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.75,0:33:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,…我们有什么回报？\Nbut you think we'll get hazard pay out of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.21,0:33:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你是想说服我 他们是合适人选，那还是省省吧\NIf you're trying to make me feel better about this scenario, give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.80,0:33:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,老实说，我很乐观\NTo tell you the truth, I'm kind of encouraged. This guy Chick here...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.26,0:33:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,奇克当过六年的飞行员\Nwas an Air Force commando for six years.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.51,0:33:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人干过抢劫、被逮捕过、还拒捕\NWe got robbery, assault, arrest, resisting arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.56,0:33:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,有一个人曾经替黑道收钱\NWe got a collection agent for the mob.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.33,0:33:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,还有两个人坐过牢\NTwo of these guys have done serious time.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.18,0:33:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-他们是这行最顶尖的人才 -我也是\NLook, they're the best at what they do.  So am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.31,0:33:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,可我没你这么乐观\NAnd I'm not so optimistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.31,0:33:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,政府每年有两千五百亿的国防预算\NWe spend $250 billion a year on defence.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.52,0:33:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,现在却得靠一群\NAnd here we are. The fate of the planet is in the hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.15,0:33:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不靠谱的痞子来拯救地球？\Nof a bunch of retards I wouldn't trust with a potato gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.20,0:33:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他们怎么决定？\NSo what's the verdict?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.74,0:34:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他们答应了，不过有几个要求\NThey'll do it. They've made a few requests though.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.12,0:34:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,什么要求？\NSuch as?  [Papers Rustling]
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.00,0:34:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,只有几个要求\NJust a few things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.51,0:34:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,很小的要求，例如说…\NNothing really big. Just Well, as an example
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.51,0:34:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,奥斯卡有几张罚单没有付\NUh, Oscar here's got some outstanding parking tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.39,0:34:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,7个州有56张罚单\NFiftysix tickets in seven states.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.31,0:34:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,让我来说，奥斯卡\NI'll tell him, Oscar. I got it.  Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.65,0:34:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,费弟有两个女友\NUh, Noonan's got two women friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.11,0:34:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,想当美国公民，不能多问\Nthat he'd like to see made American citizens, no questions asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.32,0:34:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,麦斯想要大家…再使用匣式录音带\NMax would like you to bring back eighttrack tapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.24,0:34:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-这恐怕不太可能 -还有什么？\NNot sure if that's gonna work, but let's see what else.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.99,0:34:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,奇克想到赌城的凯撒皇宫住一个礼拜\NChick wants a full week's Emperor's Package at Caesar's Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.87,0:34:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你们能告诉是谁杀了肯尼迪么？\NHey, you guys wouldn't be able to tell us who actually killed Kennedy, would ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.80,0:34:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,大熊想要住在…\NUh, Bear would like to stay at the...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.76,0:34:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,…“白马”？\NWhite Horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.97,0:35:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,白宫，是白宫\NWhite House. White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.40,0:35:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他想在白宫的林肯卧房\NYeah, he'd like to stay in the Lincoln Bedroom of the White House...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.89,0:35:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,住一个暑假\Nfor the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.73,0:35:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多就这些\NStuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.48,0:35:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,有些要求应该没有问题\NSure, I think we can take care of some of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.19,0:35:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,哈瑞\NHarry!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.32,0:35:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一件事\NYeah, one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.62,0:35:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他们以后都不想再缴税\NNone of them wanna pay taxes again.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.00,0:35:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,永远都不缴\NEver.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.92,0:35:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这是干什么的？\NWho's that for? Mr. Ed?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.80,0:35:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你敢用这扎我，我就扎你的心脏\NYou stick that in me, I'm gonna stab you in the heart with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.05,0:35:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你看过“黑色通缉令”吗？\NYou ever see Pulp Fiction?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.69,0:35:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他快死了，快点\NWe're losin' him, we're losin' him. Clear! Kaboom!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.44,0:35:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-费弟，你还好吧？ -你看我这样像是还好么？\N-Freddie, you all right?  -Does this look okay to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.53,0:35:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,还好，有点麻麻的\NDoes this look okay?  It's not all bad. It's kinda tingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.82,0:36:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,查普先生，该你了\NMr. Chapel, you're next!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.37,0:36:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,护士小姐，我只是来钻洞的\NOh, gee, lady, I just came here to drill.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.37,0:36:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,哦～我也是\NOh, so did I.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.63,0:36:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,三甘油化物指数太高\NYour triglycerides are way high,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.79,0:36:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,胆固醇量更是不得了\Nand your bad cholesterol is shockingly bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.01,0:36:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,别吃太多肥肉\NGotta lay off those pork rinds, Bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.93,0:36:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,肥你个头，给你看看吧\NPork rinds this! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.18,0:36:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,至少他们很有精神\NWell, at least they're in good spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.65,0:36:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,太简单了,你想跟我比智商？\NPiece of cake. Look, you wanna compare brain pans?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.49,0:36:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我十二岁就得奖学金 有什么了不起？\NI won the Westinghouse prize when I was 12. Big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.41,0:36:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,十九岁出版论文 那又怎样？ 二十二岁成为麻省理工学院\NPublished at 19. So what? I got a double doctorate from M.I.T. at 22.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.45,0:36:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,化学和地理双博士,我在普林斯顿大学教过两年半的书\NChemistry and geology. I taught at Princeton for twoandahalf years.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.95,0:36:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我待过最不舒服的房间\NYou know, I think this might be the most uncomfortable room I've ever been in in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.29,0:36:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我为什么要当钻油工？因为干这行能领高薪、环游世界、\NWhy do I do this? Because the money's good, the scenery changes,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.42,0:36:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,还能玩炸药\Nand they let me use explosives, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.92,0:36:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管跟我玩心理游戏\NOkay, you wanna be all psychological with me, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.76,0:37:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我受不了大家都搞不懂\NI'll tell you one thing that really drives me nuts...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.43,0:37:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,邦乔维到底是歌手还是乐团\Nis people who think Jethro Tull is just a person in the band.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.10,0:37:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,谁是邦乔维？\NWho is Jethro Tull?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.77,0:37:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我最爱吃下水:心、肺、肝\NMy favourite dish is haggis. Heart, lungs, liver.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.31,0:37:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,用羊肚包起来煮\NYou shove that all in a sheep's stomach, then you boil it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.69,0:37:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,骚得带劲儿\NThat'll put some hair on your ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.28,0:37:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有疯，我只是有点激动\NI am not crazy. I'm just a little emotional right now, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.57,0:37:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,等你问完了能给我抱抱吗？\NAfter this is over, could I, like, get a hug from you or somethin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.16,0:37:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那个女独眼龙好讨厌\NOkay, Cyclops lady is startin' to bug me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.54,0:37:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你能应付吗？\NCan you handle it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.38,0:37:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然能应付这件差事\NI mean, I can handle what I'm, you know, gonna do.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.63,0:37:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是受不了这间房间\NI can handle that, but I don't know if I can handle this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.63,0:37:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,大波霸\NWoman with large breasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.72,0:37:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,中波霸\NWoman with medium breasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.72,0:37:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这是哈瑞找我碴\NHere's Harry givin' me a hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.72,0:37:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这是他嫌我不够好\NAnd this is Harry tellin' me it's not good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.85,0:37:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这是他不让我娶他女儿\NAnd this is Harry tellin' me I can't marry his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.21,0:37:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢了\NThanks a lot. I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.52,0:37:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管发泄吧\NJust let it out.  [Crying]
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.40,0:37:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我在高中的时候 大脑受过重伤\NI suffered a major head injury when I was in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.06,0:37:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这张很像你，也是波霸\NThis one looks like you... with breasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.40,0:37:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然能应付，我能应付\NYeah, I can handle it. Yeah, I can handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.91,0:38:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,全垒打 小熊队赢得世界冠军\NA home run! The Cubs win the World Series! Ah
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.20,0:38:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不合格，不合格 全部都不合格\NFail. Fail. Depressively fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.29,0:38:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,有一个人有亚安酮反应\NOne toxicology analysis revealed Catamen.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.75,0:38:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那是效力很强的镇静剂\NThat is a very powerful sedative.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.09,0:38:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,镇静剂很常见，大夫\NSedatives are used all the time, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.17,0:38:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那药是给马用的\NThis one's used on horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.05,0:38:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他们有些人很强壮\NSome of these guys are pretty big.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.09,0:38:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,通常需要一年半时间\NIt would normally take 18 months to psychologically prepare,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.60,0:38:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,评估是否适合上太空\Nprescreen viable subjects for space travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.22,0:38:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,有些人有强烈攻击性…\NWe have seen evidence of a wide variety of territorial aggression.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.77,0:38:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的身体上得了太空吗？ 我只想知道这点\NCan they physically survive the trip? That's all I need to know here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.57,0:38:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,老实说，他们连测验都通不过\NPersonally, I don't know how they survived the tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.57,0:38:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,“核准”
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.16,0:38:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好一群太空狗熊\NTalk about the wrong stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.79,0:38:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,早安，我是威廉·夏普上校\NGood morning. I'm Colonel Willie Sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.08,0:38:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我除了要驾驶X71 登陆陨石表面以外\NIn addition to flying one of the X71 teams to that rock,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.00,0:38:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,还要训练你们在太空中 工作的心理和生理状态\Nmy job is to train you to deal with the mental and physical rigors of working in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.13,0:39:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,免得你们被吓坏了\Nso you don't freak out on the asteroid.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.93,0:39:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,美国宇航员 必须接受多年的训练\NUnited States astronauts train for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.39,0:39:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你们只有十二天\NYou have 12 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.39,0:39:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,开始之前还有什么问题吗？\NDo we have any intelligent questions before we get started?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.48,0:39:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,X71是什么？\NWhat's an X71?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.23,0:39:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这是第一次亮相\NYou're the first civilians to ever see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.23,0:39:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,X71航天飞机\NWe call 'em the X71s.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.36,0:39:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这是和空军合作的绝密计划\NIt's a top secret joint venture with the Air Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.11,0:39:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这两艘航天飞机 明天将被送到佛罗里达\NShe and her sister ship in Vandenberg are leaving for launch prep in Florida.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.87,0:39:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我想先让你们看看\NThought you oughta take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.34,0:39:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,登陆陨石的航天飞机 分别是自由号和独立号\NThe two shuttles going up are the Freedom and Independence.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.16,0:39:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,船身是钛合金打造\NHer titanium alloy impenetrable skin covers the toughest, meanest,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.46,0:39:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是史上最坚固、最先进的航天飞机\Nmost sophisticated space vehicle man has ever made.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.59,0:39:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,戴维上校和宇航员塔克\NOkay, Air Force Colonel Davis, NASA pilot Tucker...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.13,0:39:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,将驾驶独立号航天飞机\Nwill command the shuttle Independence.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.13,0:39:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,夏普上校和宇航员华特 将驾驶自由号航天飞机\NAir Force Colonel Sharp, NASA pilot Watts, shuttle Freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.84,0:39:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,武器专家古柏和哈斯负责放置核弹\NMunitions specialist Gruber and Halsey will supervise the nuclear ordinance.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.27,0:39:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,所以呢\NAnyway, I just thought
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.64,0:39:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想让你们…先见个面\Nthought you guys should meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.52,0:40:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,各位，欢迎光临失重训练中心\NGentlemen, welcome to our weightless environmental training facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.33,0:40:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要在陨石上游泳吗？ 是不是这样？\NSo we're going swimming on this asteroid. Is that what this is for?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.79,0:40:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们太空总署管这玩意叫“大穿山甲”\NHere at downtown NASA, we call this monster "Armadillo."
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.83,0:40:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会重新装上钻头\NGoing to be retrofitted with your drilling arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.84,0:40:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,在无重力状态 有八百匹涡轮马力\NShe'll turn 800 turbo horses in nearzero gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.88,0:40:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们看看\NMind if we take a look at her now?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.67,0:40:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,把塑料管拆掉 麦斯，动手吧\NAll these rubber hoses gotta go, Max. Count 'em up.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.97,0:40:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要变速器\NMake sure it's shortthrow shifters.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.89,0:40:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我这是什么？\NQuincy! Somebody tell me what this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.27,0:40:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,塑料冰淇淋勺子吗？是不是花了四百块？\NPlastic ice cream scoop? What'd that cost? About $400.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.40,0:40:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我服役这么多年 没见过你们这么差的人\NThis is about the sorriest group of people I've seen in all my entire military career.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.94,0:40:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,太空飞行会让你们惊声尖叫\NYour space flight's gonna be a brutal assault on your senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.53,0:40:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我让你们先尝尝苦头\NI'm here to give you a taste of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.40,0:40:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,太空总署有全世界最顶尖的飞行员\NNASA's got some of the finest pilots in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.91,0:40:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他们保证会让你们脑袋充血\NThey're gonna be suckin' your eyes into the back of your heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.37,0:40:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,飞慢点，这是我的第一次\NGo easy on me, okay? It's my first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.08,0:40:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,老实说，我有点怕坐飞机\NI just wanna seriously say I have a small fear of flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.13,0:41:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我要让你们旋转\NI'm gonna twist ya.  [Screaming Continues]
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.55,0:41:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-倒转 -你在搞什么？\NI'm gonna flip ya.  What's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.22,0:41:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,把你们晃得全身酸痛\NFrap your body till your bones hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.77,0:41:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你们尖叫 我们就飞得更快\NWhen you squeal, I'm just gonna go faster and harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.89,0:41:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,让我下去\NNo, take me down! [Screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.73,0:41:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,其他人怎样？\NHow's the rest of the crew?  Well, uh
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.44,0:41:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉我吐在你的仪表板上\NSorry about the rib chunks all over your dashboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.95,0:41:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得拍X光\NDon't forget: We gotta Xray all these
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.87,0:41:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,“星球大战”里你最想当谁？\NIf you had to say, who would you say?  I don't know, Oscar.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.58,0:41:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-不晓得，你呢？ -韩苏洛\N-Who do you think you are?  -Han Solo.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.08,0:41:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定是韩苏洛\NNo, if anybody's anybody, I'm Han.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.83,0:41:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你是邱巴卡\NAnd you're you're Chewbacca.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.84,0:41:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托！你看过“星球大战”吗？\NChewie? Have you even seen Star Wars?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.97,0:41:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,1969年 阿姆斯特朗能在月球上弹跳\NNeil Armstrong, 1969, bouncing on the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.52,0:41:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因为 月球的重力比地球小\NHe's bouncing up there because there's less gravity up there than on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.94,0:41:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,在陨石上也一样，小心点\NThis will be similar to the asteroid, so watch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.94,0:42:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,要是在上面用力弹跳\NSomething gets launched off that asteroid with enough force,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.94,0:42:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,就可能会漂到外太空\Nit's gonna keep on going right into outer space.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.40,0:42:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是也觉得 华特很性感？\NWhat is the deal? Is it just me, or is Watts really hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.16,0:42:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.16,0:42:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,新的太空衣有定向推进器\NWe have these new generation suits with directional accelerant thrusters.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.25,0:42:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会漂到外太空\NYou won't bounce like Neil Armstrong.  Yeah, think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.12,0:42:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-大熊 -是\NBear!  Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.88,0:42:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-你有问题吗？ -没有\NDo we have a problem?  No.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.00,0:42:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我正在讲解定向推进器 怎么能让你留在地面上\N'Cause I'm trying to describe to you how these D.A.T.s keep your ass on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.59,0:42:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,万一我踢你一脚\NSo that if I were to kick you in the balls,  Ooh.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.84,0:42:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你又不会用推进器 你会怎样？\Nand you don't know how to work them, what happens to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.31,0:42:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-漂到外太空 -没错\N-I float away.  -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.93,0:42:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这个训练几时开始？\NAnd when do we start training for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.89,0:42:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你们30秒戴好头盔\NGentlemen, I'll give you 30 seconds to put your helmets on.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.48,0:42:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,然后把氧气吸光\NThen the oxygen will be sucked out of this vacuum,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.77,0:42:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你们就会知道在外太空的滋味了\Nand you will know what it's like to be in space. Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.74,0:42:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,30秒后减压\N[Man On P.A.] Depressurize in 30 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.41,0:42:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,打开主阀门\NMain valves have been activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.94,0:42:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真空状态
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.72,0:43:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,“6天11小时”
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.64,0:43:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,各位，这就是飞行计划\NOkay, gentlemen, so here's the flight plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.10,0:43:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,大家别笑 我知道这不合比例\NNow let's keep the laughter to a minimum. I know this is not to scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.97,0:43:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,两艘航天飞机将于周二傍晚六点半发射\NBoth shuttles will take off Tuesday at 6:30 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.19,0:43:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,67分钟后\NNow 67 minutes later,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.73,0:43:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,到俄国空间站和宇航员安卓普会合\Nyou're gonna dock with the Russian space station to meet cosmonaut Andropov...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.65,0:43:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他会替航天飞机加液化氧\Nwho will refuel the shuttles with liquid O2.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.74,0:43:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是燃料\NThat's your fuel. Then you'll release...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.45,0:43:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,然后再花六十小时飞到月球\Nand take a 60hour trip toward the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.33,0:43:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,只有一个机会能登陆陨石\NNow we only have one shot of landing on this rock,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.58,0:43:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是当陨石经过月球的时候\Nand that's precisely when the asteroid passes by the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.13,0:43:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,利用月球引力和火箭推力\NYou'll then use lunar gravity and burn your thrusters,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.13,0:43:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,让航天飞机绕过月球\Nslingshotting you around the moon,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.63,0:43:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,飞到陨石后面\Ncoming up behind the asteroid.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.10,0:43:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-这时的重力将达到11G -我记得这段\N-You'll be upward of 11 Gs.  -Yeah, I remember this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.47,0:43:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,大灰狼被绑在火箭上\NIt's where the coyote sat his ass down in a slingshot...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.94,0:44:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,用大弹弓把自己射出去\Nand he strapped himself to an Acme rocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.90,0:44:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们也是这样吗？ -色狼\NIsls that what we're doin' here?  Rockhound.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.32,0:44:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我很认真，因为大灰狼的下场很惨\NNo, no, really, because it didn't work out too well for the coyote, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.94,0:44:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信我们的火箭 比大灰狼的好\N[Overlapping Chattering]  Actually, we have a lot better rockets than the coyote.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.66,0:44:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,完成这个动作以后\NNow when you've finished...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.66,0:44:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,航天飞机\Nyour Road Runner thrust move,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.50,0:44:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,就以22500英里的时速\Nyou'll be moving at 22,500 miles per hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.42,0:44:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,飞向那颗陨石后面\NComing around behind the asteroid,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.59,0:44:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,希望这时月球引力 已经吸掉陨石尾部\Nwhere we're hoping that the tail debris will be cleared by the moon's gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.71,0:44:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,让你们顺利降落在这里\NAnd you'll land right here. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.01,0:44:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,两艘航天飞机分别降落在\NWe got separate landing sites for each team.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.55,0:44:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,地质条件最好的地方\NSoftest parts of the rock as we can figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.43,0:44:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们准备两组人马 太空总署绝不冒险\NAt NASA, we don't take chances. We double up on everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.27,0:44:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,谁先钻到八百英尺谁就赢\NFirst team that hits 800 feet wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.06,0:44:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,陨石很大，有重力 应该可以行走\NNow this rock is big, dense. It's got some gravity. You can walk around,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.15,0:44:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不过还是用定向推进器比较轻松\Nbut use your thrusters so you can work easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.78,0:44:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,楚门先生，要是成功降落\NOkay, Mr. Truman, let's say that we actually do land on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.99,0:44:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,上面会是什么情况？\NWhat's it gonna be like up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.57,0:44:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,阳光下200度，背光处零下200度\NTwo hundred degrees in the sunlight. Minus 200 in the shade.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.49,0:45:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,布满尖石的峡谷、重力不稳定\NCanyons of razorsharp rock. Unpredictable gravitational conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.46,0:45:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,地面会突然喷发，大概就是这样\NUnexpected eruptions. Things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.42,0:45:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是最可怕的环境\NOkay, so the scariest environment imaginable. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.13,0:45:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你这么说我就懂了 最可怕的环境\NThat's all you gotta say: scariest environment imaginable.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.72,0:45:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你们钻好洞 放下核弹就离开\NOkay, so you drill, you drop the nuke and you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.84,0:45:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,最重要的是\NNow here's the key. You're gonna remote detonate the bomb...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.47,0:45:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,要在陨石到达这里之前 就用摇控器引爆核弹\Nbefore the asteroid passes this plane, zero barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.23,0:45:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这是最后屏障\NYou do that, and the remaining pieces of rock...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.11,0:45:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这样一来陨石碎片就会擦肩而过\Nshould be deflected enough to pass right by us.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.44,0:45:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,要是突破最后屏障才引爆\NNow if the bomb explodes after zero barrier,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.83,0:45:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都完了\Ngame's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.99,0:45:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这是休斯顿，发射火箭\NPaul, this is Houston, fire your rockets!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.50,0:45:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,全速前进\N[Imitating Rocket Blasting]  Okay, your rockets are maximum.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.37,0:45:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-奥斯卡 -哈瑞，怎么了？\NOscar!  Hey, Harry. Hey, how's it goin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.63,0:45:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到葛瑞丝吗？\NHave you seen Grace?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.46,0:45:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,她跟小杰在停机棚\NYeah, she's over in the hangar with A.J.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.17,0:45:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，你说葛瑞丝吗？ 我还以为你是说大熊\NHarry, wait a second. Did you say Grace? Okay, I thought you said Bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.38,0:46:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你原意嫁给我吗？\NWill you marry me?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.23,0:46:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,哈瑞，她都能投票了\NGrace is old enough to vote, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.23,0:46:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,她也能喝酒、结婚和离婚\NShe's old enough to drink or get married if she wants to, get a divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.28,0:46:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉你们\NLet me tell you something, fellas.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.84,0:46:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,等我完成任务回到地球\NWhen I get back, when we get this job done,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.53,0:46:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我会用自己的方法处理这件事\NI will deal with this in my own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.53,0:46:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是替小杰说话\NCome on, Harry. It's not like I'm rootin' for A.J. here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.74,0:47:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是说她不是小孩子了\NI'm just sayin', Grace is not a little girl any more.  Hey, Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.75,0:47:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，色狼 我去拿笔\NWait a minute. Let me get a pencil and a piece of paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.75,0:47:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,记下你的金玉良言\NI wanna jot down all your pearls of wisdom here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.75,0:47:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,老实说，当我们到处奔波时\NGet serious, Harry. Come on. While we're off trottin' the globe, hunting mud,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.34,0:47:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,她已经长得亭亭玉立了\NGracie grew up to become a fullblown hottie, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.13,0:47:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-她是个大美女 -超级辣妹\N-Harry, she is fully hot. -She is  She's a babe.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.30,0:47:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托！你们说的是我女儿\NMax, okay, you're talkin' about my little girl, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.43,0:47:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我对她很了解，好吗？\NI think I know who and what she is, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.06,0:47:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只是说 你女儿长大了\NHarry, all we're sayin' is, we're talkin' about a kid who's comin' into her own right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.89,0:47:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-她对身体很好奇 也会探索性欲 -你知道吗？\N-She's gettin' curious about her body, and she's exploring her sexuality.  -You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.57,0:47:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这很自然\NOscar.  That's a natural thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.86,0:47:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你只比她大五分钟 我干嘛听你的\NYou are about five minutes older than Grace is. Why should I listen to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.53,0:47:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我知道荷尔蒙\NI know what it feels like to have your hormones pullin' you in just...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.24,0:47:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,会让人把持不住\Na thousand different directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.24,0:47:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你不要介意 我们帮忙把她养大\NNo disrespect, man, but we all helped to raise her.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.41,0:47:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,都拿她当女儿\NSo, in part, we all feel like a bunch of daddies here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.66,0:47:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\NThat's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.83,0:47:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我辛苦工作这么多年 不是让我女儿嫁给一个粗人\NI'll be damned if I worked all these years so my little girl can marry a roughneck.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.92,0:47:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,她应该比我有出息\NShe's better than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.55,0:47:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,她比我们都有出息\NBetter than all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.08,0:48:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,(穿山甲测试地点)
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.40,0:48:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,坐好，放轻松 我会让你大开眼界\NHarry, just sit back, relax. I'm gonna put on a free Armadillo driving clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.70,0:48:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,两艘航天飞机都有钻洞小组\NTwo shuttle teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.74,0:48:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,小杰、奥斯卡、费弟和大熊 负责独立号的钻头\NA.J.'ll be running the drill team with Oscar, Bear and Noonan on the Independence.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.83,0:48:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我、奇克、麦斯和色狼 负责自由号的钻头\NI'll run the drill team on Freedom with Chick, Rockhound and Max.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.21,0:48:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,登陆后只有八个钟头钻洞\NOnce we land, we'll have eight hours to get the job done.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.50,0:48:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得钻八百英尺 才能把陨石炸成两半\NIn order to split this rock on the fault line, we're gonna have to drill to 800 feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.17,0:48:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,大家准备好了 开始进行水底模拟训练\NLet's get our game faces on. Now it's time for underwater simulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.72,0:48:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,独立号加油，快点 我们是青年队，年轻力壮\N[A.J.] Come on. Let's keep it up. Let's go. We're the younger team here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.98,0:48:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,转速加到一万一千\NWe're on the varsity team. Take it to 11,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.27,0:48:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要考考他\NOkay, gentlemen, we're gonna trick 'em up. My computer will simulate...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.27,0:48:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,在625英尺模拟天然气层,635英尺模拟铁氧层\Na gas pocket at 625 feet and then hard iron ferrite at 635.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.24,0:48:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我要增加液化氧,加速吧\NI'm gonna drill some more. We're takin' her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.32,0:49:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-我要加强动力 -不错，慢慢来\NI'm givin' it more torque right now.  All right, lookin' good, Bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.41,0:49:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,注意时间，独立号\NClamp it down. Watch your time, Independence team.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.58,0:49:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,谢了，哈瑞 让我自己作主\NThanks, Harry. Would you mind lettin' me run my own team?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.25,0:49:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,变速器会爆，慢一点\NYou're gonna blow the tranny. Slow it down, baby.  Take it easy, Bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.46,0:49:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,放心，大熊，没问题\NJust relax. She can handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.92,0:49:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,到了六百英尺，钻管太长 把转速减到八千\NA.J., you're at 600 feet. Your pipe is long. Let's back the R.P.M.s down to 8,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.01,0:49:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,没有时间了\NWe don't have time for 8,000!  A.J., take it back down.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.30,0:49:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你不减低转速 钻管或是变速器就会爆掉\NYou're gonna snap the pipe. I don't wanna blow this transmission.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.68,0:49:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-可恶，一万一千 -慢一点，小杰\NDamn it, 11,000.  Slow it down, A.J.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.89,0:49:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,大熊，有点志气\NBear, come on. Get on our team for a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.31,0:49:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,太空牛仔\NOh, space cowboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.40,0:49:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-你听到吗？ -我在听\N-Harry, are you listenin' to this?  -Yeah, I'm listenin', Bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.23,0:49:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,别管哈瑞，你要听我的\NYou don't work for Harry any more, okay? Out there, you gotta listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.69,0:49:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,在陨石上面是我作主\NWhen we're on that rocket, you gotta do what I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.36,0:49:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,转速加到一万一\NI'm throttling up to another 1,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.16,0:49:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,别冲动，变速器会爆掉\NA.J., back it off. You're gonna blow the transmission.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.83,0:49:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,哈瑞，让我决定\NHey, Harry, would you let me run my team, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.79,0:49:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,转速太高\NR.P.M.s are at red line.  Bear, goddamn it, I know what I'm doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.41,0:49:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道状况，机器没问题 相信我\NCome on. She can handle this. She'll be fine. Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.62,0:49:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-小杰，听好 -一号变速器爆掉了\N-A.J., back down.  -The number one transmission is down.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.38,0:49:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,电脑搞错了，我没有做错\NOh, son of a The computer's wrong, and you know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.42,0:50:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要重新来一次\NWe did the right thing.  We're gonna restart the simulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.22,0:50:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你想换人就要趁早\NIf you wanna replace a member of the crew, now is the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.51,0:50:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我会处理的,奇克，叫他们出来\NI'll take care of this. Get him out of the tank, Chick.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.52,0:50:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-你想回家吗？ 你想被开除吗？ -不想，\N-You wanna go home? Is that it? You wanna be fired?  -No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.90,0:50:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-我的小组没有做错 -你的小组？\N-My crew was doing the right thing.  -Your crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.15,0:50:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你的小组把变速器爆掉了\NYeah.  Your crew just blew the transmission, A.J.!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.40,0:50:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,电脑太小心了\NListen, that NASA computer is just playin' it safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.32,0:50:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你设计的钻头承受得住\NThe machine you built the rig could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.28,0:50:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴，给我闭嘴\NShut up. Just shut up! Shut your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.49,0:50:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那些人绝对不会让你凭着直觉为所欲为\NThose men in that room have zero tolerance for showin' off, hot doggin',
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.08,0:50:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,或是逞英雄，明白吗？\Ngoin' by your gut instinct or you tryin' to be a hero, you got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.17,0:50:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-说话啊，小杰 -我明白了\N-Say the words, A.J.!  -I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.13,0:50:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-我要他们明天休息一天 -休息，什么意思？\N-I want my men to have tomorrow night off.  -What do you mean "off"?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.18,0:50:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,放松，好好地休息十个钟头,然后再出发到佛罗里达\NI mean, off. Out of here. For at least ten hours. Then we'll go to Kennedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.14,0:50:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这是不可能的，太冒险了\NWell, there's no possible way we can do that, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.14,0:50:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他们也许会泄密\NThere's a potentially huge security risk. What if they talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.64,0:50:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-或者是受伤 -他们也许会太紧张办不了事\N-What if they get hurt?  -What if they're too burnt out to do the right thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.81,0:50:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,或是忘了这项任务的目的\NWhat if they get up there, and they forget what they're fighting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.36,0:50:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你也看到，他们就快崩溃了\NYou see what's goin' on. These boys are ready to snap.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.03,0:50:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他们并不想去 只是逼不得已\NThey didn't ask to be here. They got pulled off the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.32,0:51:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,明天很可能是他们在地球上的最后一天\NFor all we know, tomorrow night could be the last night they ever see Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.99,0:51:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,让他们陪陪家人并不过份吧\NI don't think it's too much to ask to let 'em spend it with their families.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.32,0:51:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-这是不可能的 -你有家人吧，上校？\NListen, there's no possible way we can do that.  You got family, Colonel?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.91,0:51:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-两个女儿 -难道你不想陪陪她们吗？\NTwo girls.  Wouldn't you like to spend tomorrow with your girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.50,0:51:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是请求，我要你照办\NI'm not askin' ya. I'm tellin' ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.58,0:51:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你想办法\NMake this happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.35,0:51:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你借这么多钱，难道不数一下吗？\NThis is a pretty big loan. Why don't you count the cash?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.89,0:51:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了，这里看起来有十万元\NNah, this looks like 100 grand to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.89,0:51:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,当然了，我要收六成利息 你最好小心点\NI'm givin' you this at 60 percent. I hope you know what you're doin',
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.27,0:51:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我拿不到钱 就会敲碎你的脑袋\Nbecause I'll bust your head with a sledgehammer.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.90,0:51:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-放心啦，我会还钱的 -我看你的气色很差\N-You'll get your money back.  -You don't look too healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.65,0:51:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会死掉吧？\NYou're not gonna die on me, are ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.61,0:51:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都可能会死,谢了\NLet's just say, no more than you are. Thanks, Vic.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.04,0:51:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,* Don't wanna close my eyes *
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.25,0:51:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,* I don't wanna fall asleep *
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.80,0:52:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,* 'Cause I'd miss you, baby *
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.88,0:52:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,* And I don't wanna miss a thing *
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.93,0:52:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-你知道我在想什么吗？ -什么？\N-You know what I was thinkin'?  -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.72,0:52:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为动物饼干不算咸饼干\NI really don't think that the animal cracker qualifies as a cracker.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.68,0:52:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-为什么？ -因为是甜的\N-Why?  -Well, 'cause it's sweet, which to me suggests cookie.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.06,0:52:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,咸饼干\NAnd, you know, putting cheese on something is sort of the defining characteristic...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.77,0:52:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,通常都放乳酪\Nof what makes a cracker a cracker.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.24,0:52:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我突然想到的\NI don't know why I thought of that. I just
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.24,0:52:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你真会甜言蜜语\NBaby, you have such sweet pillow talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.91,0:52:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这算是饼干动物奇观\NI got a little animal cracker, Discovery Channel thing happenin' right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.37,0:52:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,羚羊在平原上吃草\NWatch the gazelle, as he grazes through the open plains.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.42,0:52:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,现在印度豹偷偷爬过去\NNow look, as the cheetah approaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.59,0:52:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,看它怎么跟踪猎物\NWatch, as he stalks his prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.92,0:52:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,羚羊有所警觉\NNow, the gazelle's a little spooked,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.76,0:52:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,它可以向北\Nand he could head north to the ample sustenance...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.60,0:52:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,逃到两座山峰之间丰沃的草原\Nprovided by the mountainous peaks above.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.77,0:52:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,它也可以逃往南方\NHe could go south.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.69,0:53:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这时羚羊面对最困难的抉择\NThe gazelle now faces man's most perilous question:
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.95,0:53:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,北\NNorth...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.41,0:53:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,或南\Nor south?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.49,0:53:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,神秘的处女地\NWay down under.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.96,0:53:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,下周请继续收看\NTune in next week.  [Giggling]
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.26,0:53:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你想现在这个世界上\Ndo you think it's possible that anyone else in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.34,0:53:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,有人也像我们这样吗？\Nis doing this very same thing at this very same moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.35,0:53:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,希望有\NI hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.73,0:53:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,要不然我们拯救地球干嘛？\NOtherwise, what the hell are we tryin' to save?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.23,0:53:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,* Don't wanna close my eyes *
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.74,0:53:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,* I don't wanna fall asleep 'cause I'd miss you, baby *
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.95,0:53:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,* And I don't wanna miss a thing **
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.05,0:54:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么来了？\NWhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.05,0:54:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我正好路过…\NI was just passin' by on the, uh
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.47,0:54:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,想来…\NI came
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.18,0:54:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他是谁？\NWho's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.18,0:54:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个推销员\NThat man's a salesman.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.02,0:54:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子，进屋去好么\NWould you go inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.44,0:54:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.86,0:54:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他长高了\NHe got big.  [Door Closes]
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.41,0:54:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能随便跑来 法院禁止你来访\NYou can't come around like this. The court says you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.54,0:54:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-这对他不好 -我知道，我…\N-It confuses him.  -No, I know. I just
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.38,0:54:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想说…\NI wanted to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.76,0:54:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起，\Nthat I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.63,0:54:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉\Nabout everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.89,0:54:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我要做一件事，一件大事\NI got somethin' comin' up. It's somethin' kinda big.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.64,0:54:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你会以我为荣\NYou just might be proud of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.64,0:55:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,请你把这个给他\NWould you do somethin' for me? Would you just give him this?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.86,0:55:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你不必说是我给的\NYou don't have to You don't have to tell him who it's from. Just
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.74,0:55:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,* Everybody talkin' about what it is, what it ain't *
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.20,0:55:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,* Kiss on the devil and you piss off a saint *
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.46,0:55:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,* But it can't be love if you don't have to crawl *
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.54,0:55:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,* You say you only love him but you got to have it all *
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.01,0:55:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,费弟，你要一万块吗？\NHey, Noonan, you need ten grand?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.30,0:55:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,总得替她们付学费吧\NWe gotta put these girls through college.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.72,0:55:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,当宇航员真爽\NI love this astronaut stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.68,0:55:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个好差事\NGood work, if you can get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.76,0:55:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我是来接受宇航员训练的\NYeah, I'm just in town doin' a little astronaut training.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.43,0:55:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,太空英雄\NOoh! Astronauta.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.69,0:55:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我是任务专家\NAh, si. I'm a mission specialist.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.69,0:55:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-那是什么意思？ -不知道\NYes, and what's that mean?  I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.90,0:55:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你们算是什么东西，\NHey! Who the hell do you think you guys are?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.28,0:55:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,竟敢这么嚣张？\NYou're hoggin' all the action.  Hey, pinhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.37,0:55:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,傻瓜，去玩自己吧\NWhy don't you go find your own party?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.91,0:55:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,别这么自私\NWhy don't you spread the wealth, pal?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.58,0:55:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你这缩头乌龟\NHere. Why don't you go buy yourself a neck?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.41,0:56:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,秃头佬\NHey, Mr. Clean!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.71,0:56:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,去问问太空总署 我们是宇航员\NCall NASA! They'll confirm it! We're astronauts!  Get over there. Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.97,0:56:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们是宇航员 -我们全都是宇航员\N-Yeah, we're astronauts!  -Yeah, we're all astronauts.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.05,0:56:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,事关国家安全 明天一早你就被开除了\NYou are so messing with national security right now, man. You are fired tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.89,0:56:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去找中情局和调查局\NI'm telling ya. I'll get the C.I.A. and the F.B.I.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.73,0:56:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你只能去当玩具城的警卫\NYou'll be workin' security at Toys 'R' Us.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.85,0:56:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,再见，太空英雄\NOh, oh, baby, no, no. No, no!  Byebye, little astronaut.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.86,0:56:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不要走,我要上太空不再回来了\NOh, don't leave, baby. No, no, no. See, I'm goin' into space, and I'm not comin' back.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.53,0:56:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,它的时速三万英里\NIt's coming in at 30,000 miles an hour!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.66,0:56:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-它会撞到哪里？ -东亚,11分钟\N-Give me a projected impact.  -East Asia, 11 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.58,0:56:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们得警告… -警告谁？整个东南亚吗？\N-We're gonna have to warn  -Warn who? The entire South Pacific?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.09,0:57:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,“陨石危机公开”
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.22,0:57:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,全世界都知道了\NSo the whole world knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.39,0:57:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我你没有让人失望过\NTell me you've never let anybody down before.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.14,0:57:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有放弃过，怎么样？\NI never quit yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.44,0:57:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,只好这样了\Now's that?  I guess that'll have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.11,0:57:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗？\NYou know somethin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.48,0:57:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我还记得我进来的第一年\NI still remember the first, middle and last name...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.65,0:57:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,每个宇航员的姓名\Nof every guy that qualified for the astronaut programme first year I was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.58,0:58:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我却只能进工程部 这是没办法的\NThanks. I went into the engineering programme. Kinda had to.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.58,0:58:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,可是我好想上太空\NBut boy, I wanted to go up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.37,0:58:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我想在衣袖别上宇航员臂章\NI wanted to be one of those guys with a mission patch on my arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.84,0:58:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我很想跟你一起上去\NI tell you, I'd be on that shuttle with you, Harry, if I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.55,0:58:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你和我都不想上去\NYou don't want to be up in that shuttle any more than I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.18,0:58:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你明天好运\NGood luck in Florida tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.81,0:58:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,有五万人丧命…\N[Female Newscaster #1] The death of 50,000 people in Shanghai yesterday has rattled
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.98,0:58:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,法国卫星探测到…\N[Male Newscaster #1] A French satellite has tracked an object in space
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.10,0:58:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,(佛罗里达肯尼迪太空中心)
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.19,0:58:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,海啸高达五百英尺\N[Female Newscaster #2] Sources are estimating that the tidal wave was five
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.95,0:58:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,CNN在佛罗里达为您报导\N[Male Newscaster #2] This is CNN, live in Florida.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.95,0:58:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,太空总署进入军事戒备\NWe have just learned that NASA is on a fullscale military alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.83,0:58:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这叫做地球杀手\NThey're calling this a global killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.04,0:58:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,美国政府保持沉默\N[Female Newscaster #3] The government has been very tightlipped throughout this
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.12,0:58:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,五角大厦和太空总署合作\N[Female Newscaster #4] The Pentagon is getting involved at this point...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.54,0:58:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,可能要出航天任务\Nwith some kind of a project involving NASA and perhaps a shuttle mission
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.38,0:58:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,国防部官员不愿澄清\NSenior Pentagon officials refused comment, adding fuel to the speculation...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.68,0:58:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这令人怀疑事态严重\Nthat there could be a very serious problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.01,0:59:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,一组特别的宇航员 今晚抵达佛罗里达\N[Truman] We have a special team of astronauts that arrived in Florida this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.81,0:59:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,准备开始发射程序\NNASA's in emergency launch preparation in cooperation with Russian, Japanese...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.23,0:59:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,美国和法俄日等国 合作进行史上规模最大的太空任务\Nand French space agencies on the most massive joint space venture in history.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.77,0:59:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,“发射时间倒数:12小时”
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.16,0:59:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,葛瑞丝\NGracie?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.50,0:59:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到你的纸条\NGot your note.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.67,0:59:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这里干嘛？\NWhat're you doin' out here, honey?  Um, just thinkin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.22,0:59:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,想事情\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.26,0:59:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我要向你道歉\NI, um, want to apologize to you for
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.35,0:59:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不，你不必道歉\NOh, no, Grace, stop. You don't have to apologize at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.68,0:59:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我不该把你带到油井，到处奔波\NII sh I shouldn't have dragged you around on all those oil rigs.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.07,0:59:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我对不起你\NI don't think that I did the right thing with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.78,0:59:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不，我爱这种生活\NYou're wrong. I love my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.41,0:59:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱我生活中的一切\NI love everything about my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.70,1:00:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈离开我并不怪你\NAnd I don't blame you for my mother leaving.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.75,1:00:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是她抛弃我们俩\NShe left us both.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.92,1:00:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你\NAnd I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.92,1:00:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,别说你不会回来\NAnd don't talk like you're not comin' back.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.96,1:00:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,答应我你一定会回来\NPromise me that you'll come back.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.05,1:00:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-好 -说“我保证”\N-Okay.  -Say, "I promise."
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.31,1:00:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证\NI promise, Grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.73,1:00:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不会有事的，葛瑞丝\NIt's gonna be all right, Grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.44,1:00:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不嫌麻烦的话\NIf it's not too much trouble,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.15,1:00:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,请你顺便把我未婚夫带回来\Ncan you please bring my fiance home with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.57,1:00:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,老天\NOh, Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.55,1:00:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,“纪念阿波罗一号壮烈牺牲的太空英雄”
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.59,1:00:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,总统一小时后发表讲话并回答记者提问\NThe president will be addressing the nation and all of you personally within the hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.86,1:01:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,“造福全人类”
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.79,1:01:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,宇航员，来吧\NAstronauts.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.92,1:01:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,过几天见\NI'll see you in a couple days, honey.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.51,1:01:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,*收拾行囊*\N* All my bags are packed *
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.72,1:01:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,*准备出发*\N* I'm ready to go *
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.64,1:01:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,*呆呆站在你家大门*\N* I'm standin' here outside your door *  ** [Humming]
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.31,1:01:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,*我不忍心将你叫醒*\N* I hate to wake you up *
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.36,1:01:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,*向你道别*\N* To say goodbye *
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.99,1:02:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,*亲我一下对我微笑*\N* So kiss me and smile for me *
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.37,1:02:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,*让我知道你会等我*\N* Let me know you'll wait for me *
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.49,1:02:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,*紧抱着我别让我走*\N* Hold me like you'll never let me go *
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.00,1:02:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,*我要搭机*\N[Grunting] * 'Cause I'm leavin' *
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.63,1:02:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,*远离家乡*\N* On a jet plane *
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.21,1:02:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,*我不晓得何时回来*\N* Don't know when I'll be back again *
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.55,1:02:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,*搭机远离家乡*\N* Leavin' on a jet plane *
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.22,1:02:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,*不知何时回来*\N* I don't know when I'll be back again *
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.89,1:02:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,*搭机远离家乡*\N* Leavin' on a jet plane *
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.56,1:02:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,*不知何时回来…*\N* I don't know when I'll be back again *
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.90,1:02:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-*搭机远离家乡,不知何时回来…* -你瞧，楚门\N-* Leavin' on a jet plane Don't know when I'll be back again *  -So, Truman,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.57,1:02:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你就找来这群小丑拯救地球吗？\Nthis is who you found to save the planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.82,1:02:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-可以走了吧 -等一下\N-Frost, you good to go?  -Mmhmm. One One sec.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.36,1:02:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,*搭机远离家乡* -他老是吊儿郎当的\N* Leavin' on a jet plane *  That boy don't take anything seriously.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.62,1:02:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀，我记得你当年也一样\NYeah. Reminds me of a guy I used to know.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.54,1:02:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,*搭机远离家乡*\N* Aah *  * Leavin' on a jet plane *
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.08,1:02:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-*不知何时回来…* -我会娶你的\N-* I don't know when I'll be back again *  -I'm marrying you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.92,1:02:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-当然了 -*搭机远离家乡*\NBet your ass you are.  * Leavin' on a jet plane *
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.67,1:03:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,*不知何时回来…*\N* I don't know when I'll be back again **
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.19,1:03:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚\NI address you tonight,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.86,1:03:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是以美国总统的身份向各位发言\Nnot as the President of the United States,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.82,1:03:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不是一国元首\Nnot as the leader of a country,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.91,1:03:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,而是人类的一员\Nbut as a citizen of humanity.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.92,1:03:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,人类面对最大的挑战\NWe are faced with the very gravest of challenges.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.80,1:03:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,圣经说这是世界末日 万物毁灭\NThe Bible calls this day Armageddon, the end of all things.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.93,1:03:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不过这是地球史上\NAnd yet, for the first time...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.14,1:03:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,人类首次\Nin the history of the planet,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.81,1:03:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,凭自己的力量\Na species has the technology...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.48,1:03:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,避免遭到毁灭\Nto prevent its own extinction.  [Translator On TV]
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.82,1:04:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我要让大家知道\NAll of you praying with us need to know...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.74,1:04:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经尽一切努力\Nthat everything that can be done to prevent this disaster...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.20,1:04:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,避免这场浩劫\Nis being called into service.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.29,1:04:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,人类追求的\NThe human thirst for excellence,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.87,1:04:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,知识结晶\N[Translator On Radio]  knowledge,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.46,1:04:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,对科学的苦心钻研\Nevery step up the ladder of science,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.30,1:04:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,冒险飞向太空的努力\Nevery adventurous reach into space,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.22,1:04:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,现代科技的成果和想像力,甚至来自战争的经验\Nall of our combined modern technologies and imaginations, even the wars that we've fought,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.89,1:04:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,都为这场生死战\Nhave provided us the tools...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.52,1:04:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,提供武器\Nto wage this terrible battle.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.94,1:04:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,在多灾多难的历史上 人类曾经犯过多少错\NThrough all the chaos that is our history,  [Translator On TV]
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.36,1:04:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,人们曾经受过多少苦 经过这么多年\Nthrough all of the wrongs and the discord, through all of the pain and suffering,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.20,1:04:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,只有一种情操…\Nthrough all of our times, there is one thing that has...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.41,1:04:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-妈妈，那个推销员上电视了\Nnourished our souls...  Mom, that salesman's on TV.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.21,1:04:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,…能让人类继续生存下去\Nand elevated our species above its origins,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.87,1:04:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是勇气\Nand that is our courage.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.38,1:05:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,全世界的希望\NDreams of an entire planet are focused tonight...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.71,1:05:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,都寄托在这十四名勇士身上\Non those 14 brave souls...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.51,1:05:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他们将飞向太空\Ntravelling into the heavens.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.01,1:05:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他不是推销员，\NThat man's not a salesman.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.56,1:05:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-他是你爸爸 -让全球的人类目睹\N-That's your daddy.  -And may we all,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.85,1:05:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的英勇事迹\Ncitizens the world over, see these events through.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.81,1:05:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,愿上帝保佑，祝你们好运\NGodspeed and good luck to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.74,1:05:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,自由号、独立号\NFreedom crew. Independence crew.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.25,1:05:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-你还好吧？ -还好\N-How ya feelin'?  -Uh, good, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.84,1:05:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我这辈子没这么害怕过\NI mean, considering I've never been this scared in my entire life. I You know
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.13,1:05:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,上去了你就得靠自己\NListen. Once you get up there, you're gonna be on your own.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.80,1:05:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-要是发生什么事… -我知道，哈瑞\N-If anything should happen, I just wanted to  -I know, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.93,1:05:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我会试着不让你失望\NI'll, uh, try not to disappoint you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.56,1:05:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你要保重，小子\NTake care of yourself, kid.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.86,1:06:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,自由号到了\N[Man #1] Freedom's on the bridge. Attention in the firing room.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.61,1:06:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-注意了，氧化剂完成输入 -独立号到了\NOxidizer loading is complete.  [Man #2] Independence on the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.74,1:06:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,请注意，倒数计时两小时\N[Man #1] Attention all personnel. We are T minus two hours to the programme goal.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.55,1:06:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-哈瑞 -怎么了？\N-Hey, Harry.  -Yeah, Rock?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.39,1:06:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有四百万磅燃料 一枚核弹\NYou know, we're sittin' on four million pounds of fuel, one nuclear weapon...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.81,1:06:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,和一个庞大复杂的钻头\Nand a thing that has 270,000 moving parts...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.93,1:06:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,由出价最低的承包商制造\Nbuilt by the lowest bidder. [Grunts]
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.39,1:06:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-真是让人放心，对吧？ -是啊\N-Makes you feel good, doesn't it?  -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.73,1:06:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-你觉得如何，奥斯卡？ -很棒\N-How ya doin', Oscar?  -Great.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.32,1:06:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我既兴奋又害怕\NI got that excited, scared feelin'
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.82,1:06:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,九成兴奋，一成害怕\Nlike 98 percent excited, 2 percent scared.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.03,1:06:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,也许正好相反,也许是九成害怕，一成兴奋\NMaybe more. It could be 2 It could be 98 percent scared, 2 percent excited.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.12,1:07:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我才这么激动紧张 我也搞不清楚\NBut that's what makes it so intense, is it's so confused. I can't really figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.96,1:07:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,请绑紧点，我不想掉下来\NWill you make mine really tight, 'cause I don't want to fall out?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.88,1:07:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,最好紧得快要把我勒死\NI mean, almost to the point of cutting off circulation.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.80,1:07:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,要是太空总署倒闭\NIt must be a comfort to know that if the space programme goes under,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.93,1:07:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以去当驯兽师\Nyou can always get a job at Helga's House of Pain, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.31,1:07:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是发射中心 报告准备情况\NAll right. Flight directors on with the go/nogo for launch.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.85,1:07:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,-返航？推进器？ -就绪 -就绪\NRetro. Booster.  Go flight.  Go flight.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.35,1:07:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-导航系统？程序小组？ -就绪 -就绪\NEcos. Trajectory.  Go flight.  Go flight.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.15,1:07:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,救援系统？\NFIDO. EVA.  Go flight.  Go flight.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.86,1:07:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-自由号通讯系统？ 独立号通讯系统？-就绪\NCAPCOM Freedom. CAPCOM Independence.  Go flight.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.40,1:07:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-就绪 -各位，一切就绪\NGo flight.  All right, ladies and gentlemen, it's pucker time.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.87,1:07:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,自由号和独立号 这是发射中心 倒数计时一分钟\NIndependence and Freedom, this is Kennedy firing room. We're T minus one minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.62,1:07:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,大家把护镜放下来\NAll crew members, close and lock your visors.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.21,1:07:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,独立号，系统一切正常\NIndependence, this is launch control. Be advised, we're in a smooth count.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.88,1:07:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,倒数31秒，启动自动程序\NT minus 31. You're go for autosequence start.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.05,1:07:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,飞行员，启动辅助电源\NP.L.T.s, perform your A.P.U. prestart.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.59,1:07:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,各位，你们都是战士.上帝保佑你们\NOkay, gentlemen, you're our warriors up there. God be with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.18,1:07:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你们都是英雄 好好享受这一趟\NYou're already heroes. Just sit back and enjoy the ride.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.90,1:08:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,倒数20秒\NWe're T minus 20 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.57,1:08:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten. Nine. Eight. Seven.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.86,1:08:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Four. Three. Two. One.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.95,1:08:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,主引擎启动\N[Roaring]  We have main engine start.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.08,1:08:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,点燃推进火箭\NWe have booster ignition.  We're going.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.71,1:08:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And liftoff.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.01,1:08:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Freedom, this is flight deck.  [Sharp On Radio]
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.43,1:08:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,情况不错\NRoger, Freedom. You're looking good.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.32,1:08:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,独立号准备发射 -三、二、一\NWe have go for Independence.  Three. Two. One.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.28,1:08:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,升空\NIndependence, we have booster ignition.  [Chattering Continues]
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.41,1:09:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,升空了，休斯顿\NWe have liftoff.  We are cooking, Houston.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.69,1:09:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,休斯顿，发射成功 交给你们了\NHouston, the tower is clear. They're all yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.32,1:09:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,打起精神，我们接手\N[Shuttles Roaring]  Heads up, everybody. They're ours now.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.49,1:09:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-引擎运作正常 -两艘航天飞机都要注意\N-All engines are go.  -Keep a sharp eye out on both of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.96,1:09:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,进行翻转动作\N[Sharp] Start roll manoeuvre.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.51,1:09:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,翻转成功,很顺利,最高压力\NTwo good roll programmes.  One down.  Independence, we have max cue.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.89,1:10:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,现在达到最高压力\NRoger, Control. We are a max cue.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.94,1:10:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,抛弃固体火箭推进器\NS.R.B. sep  [Engines Roaring]
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.53,1:10:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-切断主引擎 -收到\N-We are singleengine, press, demigo.  -Copy, press, demigo.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.90,1:10:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,休斯顿，这趟真过瘾\NHouston, this is a kickass ride!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.87,1:10:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,自由号，主引擎按时切断\NFreedom, this is Houston. Main engine cut out on schedule. Out.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.22,1:10:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,自由号,状态很好\NFreedom, stats are good.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.89,1:10:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天\NIndependence, telemetry is up and running.  Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.94,1:10:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-这是太空 -还不算什么\N-This is space! -'Course, we're just in the beginning part of space.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.86,1:10:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都还没到外太空\NWeWe haven't gotten to outer space yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.44,1:10:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到空间站了 点燃减速火箭\NRoger, Houston. We have a visual on the Russian space station. Initiating retro burn.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.41,1:11:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,各位，空间站在外太空 已经有十一年了\NGentlemen, remember the Russian space station has been up there for 11 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.16,1:11:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的车都没这么旧\NMost of us don't have cars that old.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.58,1:11:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,宇航员在里头待了一年半 只有一个人\NNow, the cosmonaut on board has been on that tin can for 18 months, alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.92,1:11:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他一定会有点古怪\NSo don't be surprised if he's a little... off.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.92,1:11:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,各位，\NIndependence, we're gonna put you  All right, crew.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.76,1:11:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,脱掉飞行衣\NLet's exit these flight suits.  [Laughing]
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.26,1:11:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,大家好，\N[Russian Accent] Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.80,1:11:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这是俄国空间站 听到吗？\NThis is Russian space station. Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.77,1:11:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你好，我们收到 这是休斯顿\N[Speaks Russian] We copy, Russian space station. This is Houston.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.94,1:11:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我准备启动推进器\NI'm ready to fire my thrusters any time.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.61,1:11:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-请待命 -我哪儿都不会去\N-Stand by.  -Okay. I'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.11,1:11:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,一切就绪，进行重力旋转\NWe have a go. Initiate gravitational spin.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.12,1:11:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,完成百分之四十旋转\NYou are maxed at 40percent spin.  [Moans]
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.63,1:11:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，休斯顿\NOkay, Houston.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.42,1:11:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我开始感觉有重力了\NI can feel I'm having gravity.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.26,1:11:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,各位，马上就要连接\NAll right, gentlemen. We're gonna dock in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.18,1:12:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,俄国空间站有模拟重力\NNow, the Russian space station has fired her rockets...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.18,1:12:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这样工作起来比较快\NWhee!  to simulate gravity and let us work faster.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.64,1:12:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不过你们会有点想吐 要有心理准备\NIt's gonna make you queasy, so prepare yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.85,1:12:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,该是时候了 我有一个钟头没吐过\NWell, it's about time. I haven't thrown up in about an hour.  [Laughing]
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.40,1:12:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,进行连接程序\NInitiating first phase of docking procedure.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.74,1:12:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,换到手控 手控\NSwitching to manual.  Manual override.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.50,1:12:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,每秒一英尺，慢慢来 二十英尺\NOne foot per second. Let's take this slow and do it right, folks. Twenty feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.92,1:12:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,十英尺\N[Blipping]  Ten feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.63,1:12:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,情况很好 五英尺\NLooking good on radar. Five feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.01,1:12:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,锁住，燃料组，快走\NLocks are engaged. Fuel teams, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.73,1:12:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,自由号一切顺利\NFreedom, telemetry is looking good.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.81,1:12:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,暂时连接\N[Hissing]  We have soft dock.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.19,1:12:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,燃料组，准备出航天飞机\N[Sharp] Fuel teams, prepare to unload.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.36,1:13:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,各位，小心头\NAll right, gentlemen, watch your heads.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.37,1:13:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧，独立号\NLet's go, Independence.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.83,1:13:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,上校\NColonel.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.84,1:13:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他人呢？有人在吗？\NWhere is he? Anybody home?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.09,1:13:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎，伙计们\NWelcome, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.89,1:13:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这里不是加油站.这是我负责的先进实验室\NI am not gas station. This is sophisticated laboratory. I'm in charge.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.65,1:13:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,什么也别乱碰\NSo do not be touching anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.86,1:13:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我要…你\NI need one I need you.  Go with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.19,1:13:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-跟他去 -快点，快点，来吧\NI need you. Hurry up. Hurry up. Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.11,1:13:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你得盯着燃料仪表 穿上防冻衣\NIt's very important you watch the fuel gauge, okay? Put on cold suit.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.08,1:13:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,收到了，准备输送燃料\NCopy that, Houston. Prepping for fuel transfer.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.46,1:13:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,燃料管在下面\NFuel pod is down there.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.79,1:13:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,下面？太好了\NIt's down here, huh? Great.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.10,1:14:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,把这些接起来\NOkay, let's connect these fuel lines.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.27,1:14:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,自由号，左，独立号，右\NFreedom on the left, Independence on the right.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.81,1:14:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们到左边\NAll right. We're goin' left here.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.23,1:14:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这是燃料仪表，看好它 150、160没问题\NTo the right is fuel gauge. You watch the fuel gauge. One fifty, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.16,1:14:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,跳到200，太空站就完了\NOne sixty, okay. Two hundred, bad disaster for space station.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.33,1:14:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,跳到200就喊勒夫 把这个打开，叫勒夫\NSo if you watch 200, you call for Lev, on, and you see here number one. Off.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.96,1:14:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,然后拉下这个，拉到底\NYou ask for Lev. And you pull this down, all the way down.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.79,1:14:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-勒夫是什么？ -我就是勒夫，俄国太空上校\N-What's Lev?  -I am Lev Andropov, colonel of Russian space agency.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.84,1:14:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,在俄国是大人物\NIn Russia I'm a very big man.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.18,1:14:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,准备输送燃料\NWe're ready to transfer.  I'm coming. No problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.98,1:14:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我来了，没问题\NYou. You. You there!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.64,1:14:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,锁住,准备输送燃料\NHard locked.  Ready for transfusion!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.49,1:15:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,燃料输送中\N[Lev] Fuel is pumping.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.75,1:15:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,勒夫，压力上升，\NHey, Lev, the, uh, thethe pressure's climbing.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.42,1:15:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,有问题了\NStill, we're on fuel transference.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.50,1:15:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,别碰我叔叔\NDon't touch my uncle. You know?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.84,1:15:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他是我们家的天才\NHe's a genius of my family.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.84,1:15:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,有人听到吗？\N[Hissing]  Lev! Can anybody hear me? Guys? Hello, guys!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.85,1:15:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他专门做核弹\N[No Audio]  He used to work for a big bomb factory.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.52,1:15:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,瞄准纽约\NHe used to make the tip of the bomb, the thing...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.39,1:15:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,或是华府就轰掉\Nthat finds, uh, New York or Washington, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.44,1:15:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,有温差，检查管子\NOoh.  Check your hoses. We got some thermal variation.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.48,1:15:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,检查联轴器 我要回航天飞机\NStamper, let's look at the couplings, back on the shuttle.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.03,1:15:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好，关掉\NOkay. Shut down. Uh
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.21,1:15:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,大伙儿\NUh Guys!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.54,1:15:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,什么声音？\N[Sharp] What's that noise?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.50,1:16:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了，停下来！\NOh, no! God!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.76,1:16:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.01,1:16:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,燃料外泄\N[Shouting In Russian] Leak! Leak!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.14,1:16:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,快把他们带回航天飞机 快走\NGet your men back to the shuttle! Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.40,1:16:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,快点，快走吧\NGo! Hurry up! Get out of there!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.73,1:16:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,真是聪明,扳下手柄\NYou know, this really smarts!  Pull lever!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.24,1:16:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这个？\NThis is the lever!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.07,1:16:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-上校，快把他救出来 -小杰，快点\NColonel, we must get him out of there!  A.J., come on out!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.54,1:16:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,快点，快点\NAah! Aah!  Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.92,1:16:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,进行紧急脱离\NEmergency break away!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.04,1:16:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,燃料舱起火\NWe got a fire in the fuel pod!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.76,1:16:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-快点 -小杰被困在燃料舱\N-Come on!  Come on! Get in here! -A.J.'s stuck in the fuel pod!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.89,1:16:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,失去控制了\NWe're losing it!  [All Shouting]
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.32,1:17:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到太空站在晃动\NControl, this is Independence. I am seeing vibration
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.16,1:17:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-快报告 -情况不妙，燃料舱起火\N-Malloy, talk to me!  -Not good. We got sparks and fire in the fuel pod.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.74,1:17:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,独立号，马上离开\NIndependence, blow those locks and get outta there now!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.16,1:17:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,解开燃料管\NDump the hoses now! We're going!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.17,1:17:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事？ 停止输送了吗？ 快爆炸了，该死\NWhat happened? Let me shut off the O2 feed!  Harry, it's burnin' up!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.17,1:17:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,麦斯，快进去\NDamn! Max, Rock, get in here!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.76,1:17:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,把管子弄掉\NGet down there and crack these pipes over here!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.01,1:17:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我要回去救另一组人\NHarry, it's burnin' up!  We're goin' back for the other team!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.80,1:17:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,打开人员定位器\N[Chatter On Radio]  [Man] Switch on the personnel locators.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.06,1:17:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,小杰正爬上来\NTrackin' A.J. He's climbin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.48,1:17:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,太迟了，快回去，\NNo!  Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.02,1:17:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,快爆炸了\NIt's too late! Get back to the shuttle! This thing's gonna blow!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.86,1:17:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不！\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.32,1:17:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得快走，来呀\NColonel, we gotta move now! Come on! Close the hatch!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.86,1:17:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，里面还有人\NWait a minute! Wait a minute! We got a man in there!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.41,1:17:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,打开门我们全都会死.燃料外泄\NOpen that door, and we'll all die!  Fuel leak!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.16,1:17:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,马上撤退，快点\NEvac now! Let's go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.84,1:18:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,快回来，舱门坏了\NCome on back! No, wait! The door is broken!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.84,1:18:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,火势被密封在燃料舱\NNo!  They got the fire sealed in the fuel pod.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.34,1:18:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-火势被控制住 -快回到航天飞机\N-They locked it down.  [Man On P.A.] -Tracking men to the shuttle.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.64,1:18:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,还有两人被困在下面\NThey've still got two men trapped in there!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.48,1:18:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,快跑，离航天飞机还有75英尺.其他人呢？\NKeep running! The shuttle's another 75 feet! Where's the rest of the team?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.98,1:18:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,小杰呢？\N[All Shouting]  Where's A.J.?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.36,1:18:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-没救了 -不能丢下他\N-A.J.'s gone!  -We're not leavin' without A.J.!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.98,1:18:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,没救了，来不及了\NHe's gone! It's too late!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.95,1:18:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧，这是唯一的机会\NCome on! This way is our only chance!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.41,1:18:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,零下一百度，\NSo it's minus hundred!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.04,1:18:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,很冷 不憋气肺会被冻僵\NVery cold. Hold breath, or lung freezes!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.75,1:18:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,回到航天飞机，锁上舱门\N[Shouting]  Get back to the shuttle! And lock that door!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.05,1:18:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,小杰还在里面 起火了 救不了他们\NIt's on fire! It's on fire, Harry!  It's them or all of us!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.60,1:18:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,起火了\NIt's on fire.  Full thrust.  We're gonna get hit.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.20,1:19:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,舱门会爆炸\NLev! Lev, the door's gonna blow!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.96,1:19:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得快走\NOh!  We're going! It's gonna blow!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.76,1:19:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,小杰还在里面 快脱离 我们得快走\NA.J.'s still in there!  Blow the locks. No, the bolts!  We've gotta
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.18,1:19:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,加油，快到了\NI think we're almost there!  [All Shouting]
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.68,1:19:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,小杰没在独立号上 他们要锁住舱门\NFlight, Independence does not have A.J. They're gonna close the door without him.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.44,1:19:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他们离航天飞机 只有75英尺远\N[Man] Tracking. They're 75 feet from the shuttle.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.44,1:19:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,叫他们快一点\NJust tell 'em to air lock the door and go!  Dog the hatch now!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.40,1:19:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,关上舱门\NClose it!  [Explosion]
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.99,1:19:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,上校，掉下来了，快走吧\NWhoa, whoa, whoa! Colonel! That thing's comin' right for We got to move!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.96,1:20:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,快点，舱门快关了\NHurry up! There's the shuttle door! [Shouting]
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.80,1:20:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,起火了，关门\NFire's coming at us! Close the door now!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.81,1:20:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,快走\NGo! Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.94,1:20:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,自由号,独立号的组员全都在\NFreedom, the Independence crew is on board and accounted for.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.61,1:20:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-还多了一名俄国宇航员 -成功输送九成燃料\N-We're even heavy one cosmonaut.  -They got 90 percent of their fuel.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.70,1:20:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,挺刺激的\NPretty intense, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.83,1:20:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我才叫你们什么都别碰\NThat's why I told you, "Touch nothing."
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.20,1:20:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这些臭牛仔\NBut you're bunch of cowboys.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.71,1:20:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,全人类的焦点都集中在\NSo while the consciousness of the planet is unified,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.51,1:20:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,太空总署的航天任务\Nfocused on the NASA mission taking place right now in the vast ocean of space,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.34,1:20:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,任务正进行最后阶段\N[Speaking Russian]  we're now in the final hours of the mission,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.35,1:20:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,两艘航天飞机准备绕过月球\Nas the Freedom and Independence prepare to slingshot around the moon.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.10,1:21:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,“17时3分52秒”
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.98,1:21:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,早安，各位\NMorning, guys. It's time to suit up, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.69,1:21:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,穿好宇航服，准备干活\NUh, we got a big day.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.70,1:21:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,18秒后中断通讯 推进程序确认\NEighteen seconds to radio interrupt.  Booster sequence confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.58,1:21:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这是休斯顿，自由号 收到了\NThis is Houston. Roger that, Freedom. We copy.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.75,1:21:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,准备绕过月球\NShuttles are ready for the burn around the moon.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.04,1:21:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,通讯中断，失去联络\NRadio contact terminated. We're out.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.37,1:21:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,11分钟内到达10G重力 开始祈祷吧\NNine and a half Gs for 11 minutes. I'd start praying about right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.26,1:21:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们应该抓紧\NSo this is the part where we're supposed to just...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.05,1:21:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,希望不会死\Nhold on real tight and, uh, hope we don't die.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.77,1:21:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,准备越过月球轨道 进入月球轨道\NStand by for lunar roll.  High inclination. Lunar orbit.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.40,1:21:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你们写好遗嘱了\NYou boys got those wills filled out correctly?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.62,1:22:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,时候到了，咬紧牙关\NAll right, men, this is what we trained for. Now just suck it up!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.17,1:22:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,准备，5、4、\NOn the mark. Five. Four.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.09,1:22:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,3、2、1\NThree. Two. One.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.23,1:22:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-这样正常吗？ -别担心，很正常\N-Is this supposed to be like this?  -Don't worry. This is normal.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.90,1:22:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道？\NHow would you know? [Groaning]
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.90,1:22:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,时速一万四千哩 4G重力\NFourteen thousand miles an hour.  Four Gs.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.40,1:22:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-这会持续多久？ -6G\N-Ahh!  How long does this last?  -Six Gs.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.61,1:22:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-时速一万五千哩 -我好重 -这不正常\NFifteen thousand.  Really heavy, man!  This isn't normal.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.95,1:22:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思？ 糟糕透了\NWhat do you mean, "this isn't normal"?  This is way worse!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.41,1:22:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,8G重力，抓紧\NEight Gs. Hang tight!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.62,1:22:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-我熬不过去啦 -我们都会死的\N-We're not gonna make it! -Oh, we're gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.25,1:22:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,12分钟，没有信号\NTwelve minutes. Flight, we still got nothin' here.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.59,1:22:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,太快了\N[All Groaning]  This is too fast!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.68,1:23:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,10G\NTen Gs!  [Groaning Continues]
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.82,1:23:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,到达最高速度 时速两万两千五百哩\N[Sharp] We're maxed at 22,500!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.08,1:23:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,收到两艘航天飞机的信号\NWe have acquisition of signal from Independence and Freedom.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.79,1:23:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来\N[Relieved Chattering]  We're in, guys. All right. Welcome back, team.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.30,1:23:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我们看到目标了\NWe have visual of the target, Houston.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.68,1:23:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你们看到吗？\NYou see that?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.40,1:23:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-独立号，请回答 -休斯顿，真是不可思议\NCome in, Independence.  [Sharp] Houston, you gotta see this to believe it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.91,1:24:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-准备降落 -尾部的碎石有多少？\N-Okay, team, let's take 'em in. -Okay, Quincy, how much tail debris do we have?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.62,1:24:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,自由号，打开FOD雷达\N[Man] Freedom, turn on FOD radar.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.87,1:24:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,打开了\NFOD radar on.  [Blipping]
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.25,1:24:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,坐好了，这会很颠簸 准备躲闪\NEverybody, hang on. This could get a little rough. Engaging evasive radar.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.89,1:24:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,坐好\NHold on!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.57,1:24:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,该死，有浮石\NGoddamn! We got debris!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.45,1:24:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,抛弃辅助推进器\N[Watts] We're dumping auxiliary boosters.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.21,1:24:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,有乱流 好多浮石\NHouston, do you read me?  We got debris!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.10,1:25:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,要进去了 情况不妙\NWe're goin' in! We're comin' in hot!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.52,1:25:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,继续前往降落点\NIndependence, try to maintain your present heading. You've got a target L.Z.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.94,1:25:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-浮石太多，快躲开 -不行\N-There's too much debris! We gotta peel off!  -Negative!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.11,1:25:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们被击中\N[Loud Crashing]  We're hit!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.78,1:25:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,求救，我失去主推进器\NMayday, mayday!  I've lost main thrusters. Get 'em back up!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.95,1:25:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,求救，失去推进器\NMayday, Houston, mayday! We've lost R.C.S. thrusters!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.37,1:25:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,失去控制，就快坠毁 收到吗？我们就快坠毁\NMayday, Freedom, mayday! We are out of control! We are going down!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.46,1:25:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,自由号，小心\NDo you read me? Freedom, we are going down!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.97,1:25:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,它会撞上去\NWe're gonna hit!  [Blipping]
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.53,1:26:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,大家使用救生系统,快到货舱去\NEverybody, go to your own life support! Lock yourself in the cargo bay!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.66,1:26:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要坠毁了 休斯顿，我们失去控制 快要坠毁了\NWe are going down! Houston! Houston, we are going down! We have lost control!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.75,1:26:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我戴不上去\NI can't get it on!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.83,1:26:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你好运，自由号 我的天，完了\NGood luck, Freedom.  Oh, my God, this is it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.56,1:27:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么？是独立号吗？\NSharp, what the hell is that? Is that the Independence?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.27,1:27:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,独立号毁了，它没救了\N[Sharp] Houston, Independence is a dead stick. They're not gonna make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.71,1:27:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,独立号坠毁了\NHouston, Independence has gone down.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.18,1:27:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,准备降落，反向推动\NWhen I touch this baby down, full reverse thrust.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.72,1:27:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,给我点动力\NFires on your right, Sharp!  Reversing the thrusters!  [Thrusters Roaring]
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.89,1:27:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,坐好了\NHang tight! Hang tight!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.52,1:27:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,休斯顿，我们错过降落点…\NHouston, we overshot our landing field. We overshot our landing field.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.15,1:28:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕\NOh, no!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.06,1:28:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,进行系统检查 确定我们能返航\NInitiate system light system check. Make sure we can still get off this rock.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.53,1:28:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,电力系统损坏 启动备用系统\NOur electrical system is screwed. I'm going to backup. Fuel seals check.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.62,1:28:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,燃料筒密封、引擎密封、压力舱密封\NEngine seals check. Pressure seals check.  Oh, God. Oh!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.04,1:28:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,有人受伤吗？\NAnyone hurt?  [Panting] Where's
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.17,1:29:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,另一艘航天飞机怎么了？ 另一艘航天飞机呢？\NWhere's the other shuttle? What happened to the other shuttle?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.34,1:29:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-独立号离线了 -离线？\N-Independence is off the grid.  -"Off the grid"?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.55,1:29:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你是电脑吗？ 那是什么意思？\NWhat are you, a freakin' cyborg? What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.35,1:29:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你也看到，\NHey, you saw it yourself, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.14,1:29:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他们死了\NThey're gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.18,1:29:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,自由号请回答\NCome in, Freedom. This is CAPCOM Houston. Freedom, come in.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.11,1:29:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这是休斯顿，请回答\NThis is CAPCOM Houston. Come in, Freedom.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.57,1:29:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,让上帝照顾我们的朋友\NGod!  Let's just ask God to take care of our friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.24,1:29:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,愿他们安息 阿门\NMay they rest in peace.  Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.50,1:29:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,只有八个小时\NWe got eight hours.  [Gasps]
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.05,1:29:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们完成任务回家吧\NLet's get this job done and go home.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.34,1:29:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,没信号，\NNothin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.39,1:29:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,快回答吧\NCome on, Watts, Sharp, somebody.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.72,1:29:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这是休斯顿\NThis is CAPCOM Houston.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.68,1:29:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,自由号，请回答 这是休斯顿\NCome in, Freedom. Freedom, come in. This is CAPCOM Houston.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.69,1:30:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-你不应该留在这里 -我已经无处可去\N-Maybe you shouldn't be here.  -I don't have anywhere else to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.90,1:30:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,自由号，请回答\NFreedom, come in. This is CAPCOM Houston.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.99,1:30:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,准备工具，启动钻头吧\NAll right, let's get the tools unpacked and fire up the Armadillo.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.99,1:30:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-惯性导航系统没反应 -我知道这是哪里\NWe're not getting a damn thing on the inertial nav system.  I know where we are.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.20,1:30:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-请让开 -信号中断了\NPlease step away. Radio signal's dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.08,1:30:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我要启动备用发电机\NI'm flipping the backup generator.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.08,1:30:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,无线电只有一半的效能\NRadio signal's gonna be cut in half till we get main power back.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.54,1:30:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是202段第9区 15H32，差不了多少\NWe're in segment 202, lateral grid 9, site 15H32, give or take a few yards.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.13,1:30:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-上校错过降落点有26哩 -你怎么知道？\N-Captain America here blew the landing by 26 miles.  -How the hell do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.06,1:30:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-因为我是天才 -仪表指针乱跳\N-Because I'm a genius.  -The gauges will not read.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.89,1:30:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,附近好像有磁场\NThey're all peaked, like we're plugged into some magnetic field.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.60,1:30:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-谁想知道原因？ -快说吧\N-Well, who on this spaceship wants to know why?  [Sharp]-By all means.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.19,1:30:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,本来要降落在第8区\NThe reason we were shooting for grid 8 is because...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.73,1:30:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,因为第9区全是铁氧层\Nthermographics indicated that grid 9 was compressed iron ferrite.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.28,1:30:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你降落在铁板上了\NWhich means that you landed us on a goddamn iron plate.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.70,1:30:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你也听到了 把摇控卫星连线拿出来\NAll right. Well, you heard the man. Let's wheel out the remote satellite link.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.21,1:31:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,希望还有一艘\NWe need that radio.  Oh, God, please tell me we still got one of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.29,1:31:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,独立号没有反应\N[Computers Beeping]  [Man] Independence has flatlined.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.80,1:31:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,奥斯卡…\NOscar! Oscar!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.10,1:31:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪\NOh, God!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.35,1:32:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,有人吗？\NHello! Anyone!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.40,1:32:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,有人活着吗？救命呀\NIs anyone else alive? Somebody, help me!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.78,1:32:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,小杰\NA.J.!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.70,1:32:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-你在哪里？ -我在这里\N-Where are you?  -I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.16,1:32:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,全都死了\NLev, there's no one else.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.17,1:32:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-没有人了 -我知道\N-There's no one else.  -I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.21,1:32:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,老天\N[Bear] Oh, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.88,1:32:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-大熊，你在哪里？ -小杰…\N[A.J.] Bear, where are you?  [Bear] A.J.? A.J.?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.51,1:32:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我在前面\N[Bear] I'm in the shuttle, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.51,1:32:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-你没事吧？ -见到你真好\NAre you all right?  I'm so glad to see you, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.56,1:32:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,看到你这大丑哥真高兴\NI never thought I'd be so happy to see your ugly face.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.73,1:32:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-休斯顿，收到吗？ 这是自由号 -检查推进器\NHouston, do you read? This is Freedom.  [Sharp] Check your thrusters.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.98,1:32:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-休斯顿，收到吗？ -准备好了吗？\N[Watts] Houston, do you copy?  [Sharp] Is everyone good to go?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.05,1:33:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,到下面的峡谷去\N[Harry] Down here! In the valley!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.22,1:33:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这是最可怕的噩梦\NThis place is like Dr. Seuss's worst nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.06,1:33:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,用摇控卫星 接收的信号比较清楚\NLet's get the remote satellite. We'll get better reception up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.10,1:33:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,叫麦斯下来\N[Harry] Bring Max down. Watch yourself through here, Max.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.44,1:33:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,小心，麦斯\NThere're a couple big fissures.  To the left!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.90,1:33:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,有很多裂缝 左边，开到左边\NBring it to the left!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.45,1:33:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,色狼，过来勘查地质\N[Harry] Rockhound, you come on down here and take some readings down in the flat spot.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.66,1:33:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,氧化铁\N[Beeping]  Iron ferrite.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.38,1:33:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-连线了 -我要回来，随时待命\N-I have fire.  [Harry] Watts, I'm comin' back. Stand by.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.97,1:33:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-全都是铁，色狼 -我开始讨厌我什么都懂了\N-Mostly iron, Rockhound.  -God, I hate knowing everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.14,1:34:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证铁层一定没有50英尺深\NWell, I can pretty much guarantee it's not gonna be thicker than 50 feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.19,1:34:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-你怎么知道？ -要不然我们就完了\N-How do you figure that?  -'Cause if it is, we're screwed.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.48,1:34:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-可以吗？ -挖洞吧\N-Max, you good?  -Yeah. Just makin' hole.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.15,1:34:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-转过来 -臭外太空\N-Turn it around.  [Max] Friggin' outer space.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.53,1:34:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来不错\NIt's good.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.50,1:34:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,钻进去了，很顺利\NAll right. We're in. Another light. We're cuttin' through pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.21,1:34:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我没见过这些玩意\NThere's some stuff in here I ain't never seen.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.72,1:34:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,钻深一点\NAll right, let's punch it down!  [Metal Creaking]
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.84,1:34:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-你看到吗？ -我看到了，什么东西？\N-Hey, Harry, did you see that?  -Yeah, Max, I see it. I see it. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:40.47,1:34:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-一个钻头坏了 -退出来\N-We lost the bite in the bit.  -All right. Back it off. Back it off.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.81,1:34:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,该死\NGoddamn it!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.14,1:34:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,钢柱扭曲，退出来 好，停住\NSounds like we twisted a shank. Back it out of there, Max. Good. Good. Hold 'er there.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.03,1:34:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这就像是希腊悲剧\NWow, this is a goddamn Greek tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.91,1:35:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-钻头又不是没断过 -只钻十英尺就断？\N-We've all seen broken drill heads before.  -Not after ten feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.08,1:35:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-这种事我没见过 -现在见过了\N-I never seen one.  -Well, now you've seen one.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:04.16,1:35:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-怎么办？ -把大钻头卸下来\N-What do you want?  -Unpack the Judge.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.04,1:35:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,大熊、勒夫\N[A.J.] Bear, Lev.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.34,1:35:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只剩三个宇航员\N[Lev] We're only three astronauts left now.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.72,1:35:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不是宇航员 只是油井钻工\N[A.J.] We're not astronauts. We're oil drillers. We're not even supposed to be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.60,1:35:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？你们不是宇航员？\NWhat? You're not astronaut?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.89,1:35:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我有办法了，上来吧\NI'm getting us outta here. Get in.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.23,1:35:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-为什么？ -到穿山甲上，我有个主意\NWhy?  Just get in the Armadillo. I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.77,1:35:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是自由号，收到吗？ 休斯顿，收到吗？\NHouston, this is Freedom. Do you copy? Houston, do you copy? Freedom shuttle has
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.86,1:35:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,传送图像\N[Radio Static Hissing]  We're gettin' some scattered video feeds here.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.28,1:35:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你收到吗？\N[Watts] Houston, this is Freedom. Do you copy?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.62,1:35:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,谢天谢地，自由号 这里是休斯顿\NThank God we have you, Freedom.  Freedom, this is Houston. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.24,1:35:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-别失去信号 -有信号了\N-Don't lose 'em, Malloy.  -Sharp, I'm getting something.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.25,1:35:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-这里是自由号 我们安全降落 -在哪里？\NHouston, this is Freedom. We have landed safely.  Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.33,1:35:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,15H32\NWe are at site coordinates approximately 15H32
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.75,1:35:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,找出那个地区的资料，快点\NOkay, I want to know everything we can about that location.  Got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.84,1:35:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,电力和天线都有问题\NGet it before we lose 'em.  We're also having electric and antenna difficulties.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:54.72,1:35:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-快找机械部 -我们已经开始钻洞\N-Walter, get Mechanical on that.  -But we have commenced drilling.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.39,1:36:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,快失去信号了，用四号天线\NStevens, we're losin' him. Bring it up on four. On four.  Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.18,1:36:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,还不知道能否返航\NShuttle flight capability not yet known.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.14,1:36:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,加强信号\NBump the signal.  Bumping.  Houston. Houston.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.35,1:36:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,失去信号，试着再连线,快把卫星天线架好\NWe lost 'em. Get 'em back. Gruber, we need that hookup.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.27,1:36:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都是这么硬来的\NShow you how we do things where I come from.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.99,1:36:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,坐好\NHold on!  [Metal Crumpling]
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.30,1:36:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,装好了\NSeat it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.42,1:36:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,准备旋进去\NAll right, get ready. Max, thread it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.26,1:36:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,时间紧迫，快点\NGuys, the clock is tickin'. Let's go, go, go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.47,1:36:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,转松\NAll right! Good! Crank it loose!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.31,1:36:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,转速每秒2500 干活吧\NKeep it at 25. Let's kick a little asteroid butt!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.98,1:36:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我要加强动力\NAll right, Chick. Give me more torque on the turbine, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.10,1:36:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你要加强动力\N[Drill Whining]  [Harry] Max, I need some more power down here!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.98,1:36:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好 换到四档\NAll right, boss.  Throw it in fourth, then drop the hammer.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.49,1:36:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,钻穿这些臭屎吧\NLet's drill through this turd.  [Harry] Come on, boys.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.15,1:37:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,进度落后，动作要快 -快钻进去…把它钻穿吧\NWe gotta hop. We're fallin' behind. Dig, dig, dig. Chew this iron bitch up.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.87,1:37:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,变速器卡住\NChick, the tranny's stuck.  Harry!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.87,1:37:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？\NWhat is it?  Chick, come on! Help!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.00,1:37:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,奇克，松开离合器\NRelease the clutch!  Pull it up!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.26,1:37:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这玩意动不了\NOkay. Well, this thing's not movin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.17,1:37:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，快关掉\NNo, no, no! Shut it down! Shut it
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.56,1:37:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,没有用，哈瑞\NThis is not workin' out, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.35,1:37:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,-你没事吧？ -变速器爆了\N-Oh, are you all right?  -Oh, blew the tranny. Blew the tranny.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.36,1:37:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你，上帝\NCome on, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.40,1:37:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想请你帮帮忙\NJust a little help. That's all I'm askin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.91,1:37:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他可能听得到你\NI think we're close enough. He might've heard ya.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.16,1:37:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,坏消息 陨石经过月球前转动很稳定\NHere's the bad news. Before the asteroid passed the moon,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.42,1:37:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,35度的转轴\Nher rotation was stable at 32 degrees on an x axis.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.84,1:37:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你看看 月球引力把它推得乱转\NBut now look at this. The lunar gravity's put her in a spin.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.47,1:38:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-三个轴心都在转 -我们没想到\N-She's tumbling on all three axes. -This wasn't expected, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.89,1:38:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-这会影响通讯吗？ -会\NWhat does this do for communications?  Not good.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.72,1:38:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,只能再跟航天飞机连线七分钟\NWe'll have definite contact with the shuttle for only seven more minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.02,1:38:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-然后就会失去联络 -几时能恢复正常？\N-After that it's radio darkness.  -For how long?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.89,1:38:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,七分钟后，可能就永远失去联络\NAnd after seven minutes, we may never hear from them again.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.27,1:38:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我们试着\NBut we're trying to bounce a signal...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.90,1:38:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,用俄国的军事卫星连线\Noff a Russian military satellite, reestablish contact that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.44,1:38:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,如果失去联络,几时会丧失摇控引爆核弹的能力？\NIf we lose the shuttle com, when do we lose the ability to remote detonate that nuke?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.91,1:38:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,核弹透过军事卫星引爆\NThe weapon remote receives a signal from a Milstar satellite.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.58,1:38:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,轨道比较高，信号比较强\NHigher orbit, more powerful transmitter.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.58,1:38:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,和航天飞机连线七分钟后 还有五分钟能引爆核弹\NIf we've got the shuttle for seven minutes, we can remote detonate for an additional five.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.08,1:38:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说十二分钟后\NWhat he's trying to say, General, is that, uh, in 12 minutes' time,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.21,1:38:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,就无法再引爆\Nyou may lose the ability to detonate the nuke... permanently.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.96,1:38:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我得通知总统\NI've got to inform the president.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.17,1:38:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想知道，被困在陨石上该怎么办\NJust want to make sure you know we're stuck on an asteroid.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.22,1:38:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-你知道自己在做什么吗？ -不知道\NDo you know what you're doing now?  No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.22,1:38:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道我在做什么\NYou know what? I have no idea what I'm doing. I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.52,1:38:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,也不知道这个按钮有什么用途\NThis button I don't know what that does, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.85,1:38:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我只知道我们坠毁了\NAll I know is that we just crashed back there,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.52,1:38:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,两个朋友死了，我们离哈瑞有25哩\NI lost two of my friends, we're 25 miles from Harry's shuttle.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.48,1:39:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我不晓得他是不是活着\NWe don't know if he's alive. We don't know if he can fly. All I know is, there's a beep...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.11,1:39:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在只想找到这家伙\Non this thing and I'm trying to get us there.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.58,1:39:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,卸下变速器\NLet's get it unpacked.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.71,1:39:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-怎么了？ -我从来没碰到过这种金属\N-What's up?  -We're drilling through some kind of metal I've never seen before.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.46,1:39:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,两个钻头坏掉 第一具变速器爆掉\NIt's fried two of our drill bits, and now we blew our first transmission.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.51,1:39:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-你们钻了多深？ -帮我把变速器抬下去\NSo how deep are we?  We could use your help with the transmission, Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.51,1:39:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我得进行评估报告 现在应该钻到两百英尺\NI have an assessment report due now. We're supposed to be at 200 feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.51,1:39:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-现在钻了多深？ -你不要这么啰唆\NSo how deep are we?  Not as deep as we'll be...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.64,1:39:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,快帮忙装变速器就会钻得更深\Nwhen you quit askin' me these questions and help us load this transmission on.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.40,1:39:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-现在的深度是多少？ -那并不重要，上校\N-What is our current depth?  -Our current depth is not important, Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.98,1:39:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-重不重要由我决定 -我们得钻八百英尺\N-I'll decide what's important. -We've got 800 feet to drill.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.65,1:39:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你钻了两个半小时 现在有多深？\NYou've had two and a half hours. Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.49,1:39:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,57英尺\NWe're at 57 feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.58,1:39:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你有空的话 就帮我抬变速器\NNow, if you're not too busy, maybe you can give us a hand with this transmission.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.58,1:39:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-夏普上校 -把它抬上去，我马上回来 -夏普上校\NColonel Sharp! Get this strapped up. I'll be right back. Colonel Sharp!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:55.88,1:39:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们连上线了\NAll right. I'm coming through. We have contact. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.00,1:40:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,只能这样了\NThat's as clear as it's gonna get.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.01,1:40:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,休斯顿，这是自由号 收到吗？\NHouston, this is Freedom. Do you copy?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.38,1:40:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我正在使用摇控卫星连线\NWorking at a remote satellite link at this moment. Transmission change.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.68,1:40:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,20分钟后换好变速器 十小时后才能钻好洞\NColonel!  Twenty minutes. Puts drilling final at ten hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.43,1:40:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,到时候已经突破最后屏障 请指示\NPlease advise. That's four hours past the zero barrier. Please advise.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.27,1:40:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这算什么？ “进度表”\NWhat the hell is this? "Zero depth"?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.32,1:40:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这是哪儿来的？ 你跟谁讲话？楚门吗？\NAnd where'd this come from? Who are you talkin' to? Is that Truman?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.03,1:40:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-电话给我 楚门,钻洞就是这样\NLemme have that phone. Gimme the phone. Truman! Look, this is what happens when you drill.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.53,1:40:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不能依照空军的进度表进行\NWe cannot use your "U.S. Air Force Personnel Only" drill time card.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.70,1:40:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-这是谁写的？ -快失去信号了\NWho wrote this thing, by the way?  We're losing coms again.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.45,1:40:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他听到吗？\NLook Is he getting this? Does he hear me or What's wrong with this?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.50,1:40:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-通讯中断 -那是什么意思？\N-The com's down.  -What do you mean, "the com's down"?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.25,1:40:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们和指挥中心失去联络\N[Sharp] What do I mean? I mean we've lost communication to mission control.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.67,1:40:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那就快把变速器换好\NFine. Let's go back to the cargo bay and get the transmission
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.42,1:40:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你试过却失败了，明白吗？\NHarry, guess what. You had your shot. You didn't do it. You understand me?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.22,1:40:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你尽管用这张进度表监督\NYou can't  Why don't you stay here [Shouting]
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.89,1:40:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,或是写报告什么的，随便你\NWrite a report, why don't ya? That'll be [Shouting Continues]
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.98,1:40:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我们要把洞钻好\NMy men and I will go and get this hole dug!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.06,1:40:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是太空史上最大的错误\NYou and your men are the biggest mistake in the history of NASA.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.78,1:41:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,失去联络\N[Man] We've lost communication.  Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.57,1:41:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-现在的情况不太妙 -这还用你说\N-We're not lookin' too good right now.  -No shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.45,1:41:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得设法恢复通讯\NWe gotta get that radio back up.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.04,1:41:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,总统先生，请你做决定\N[Man] Mr. President, it's time to make a decision.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.13,1:41:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,再过五分钟 就无法摇控引爆核弹\NWe can remote detonate the bomb for only another five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.97,1:41:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-我是金将军 -是的，总统先生\N[Rings]  Yes? Kimsey here. -Yes, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.76,1:41:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也看到了\NYes, we saw that too, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.77,1:41:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,也许该等…\NBut maybe we should wait until they
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.61,1:41:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,丹，叫他们离开那里\NDan, get them out of there.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.86,1:41:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-马上撤退 -为什么？\NEvac right now.  What's goin' on here?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.87,1:41:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我奉命接管这项任务\NI've been ordered to override the system.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.79,1:41:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这算什么？\NWell, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.34,1:42:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,紧急程序\NSecondary protocol.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.26,1:42:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他们还没有钻完\NBut they haven't drilled the damn hole yet!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.27,1:42:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,总统的雇问认为钻洞来不及了\NThe president's advisors feel that the drilling isn't working.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.48,1:42:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,很可能会失去无线电信号\NAnd we've lost radio contact, maybe for good.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.36,1:42:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,再过几分钟就不能摇控引爆核弹\NWe've only got a few minutes left of guaranteed ability to remote detonate that nuke.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.49,1:42:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,再不引爆就会失去机会\NIf we don't do it now we could lose control, and we may never get it back.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.45,1:42:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,叫总统开除他的雇问\NWell, you tell the president that he better fire his socalled advisors.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.45,1:42:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,在陨石表面引爆就会失去那枚核弹\NIf you detonate that nuke on the surface, we waste a perfectly good bomb,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.91,1:42:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,和拯救地球的机会\Nand we have one chance to save this planet!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.44,1:42:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,“紧急程序”
Dialogue: 0,1:42:46.88,1:42:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-把无线电修好,我要所有的电力 -知道了\N-I need that radio. Gruber, give me everything you got now!  [Gruber] Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.06,1:42:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道，总统先生 不过我只想说\NYes, Mr. President, I understand that completely, but my point is very, very simple.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.44,1:43:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你要相信我，我了解状况\NAnd I think you need to trust me on this because I know something about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:02.02,1:43:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证，你这么做会害死大家\NI guarantee you, if you do this, you kill us all.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.86,1:43:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.24,1:43:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,将军，他找你\NGeneral, he wants you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.62,1:43:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我是金将军\NThis is Kimsey. Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.75,1:43:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，我了解\NI understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.34,1:43:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我奉命在三十秒后引爆核弹\NThe orders are to remote detonate in 30 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:26.34,1:43:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你还没告诉他们\NYou have not told them yet!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:29.97,1:43:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸在上面\NThat is my father up there!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:32.55,1:43:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道你不能这么做，你很清楚\NThis is one order you shouldn't follow, and you fucking know it!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.02,1:43:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,放开她，放开她\NLet her go. Let her go!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.85,1:43:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你的钥匙，长官\NYour key, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.61,1:43:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝保佑他们\N[Consoles Beeping]  God be with them.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.57,1:43:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢来\NSlow it down.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.28,1:43:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,“启动”
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.46,1:44:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,哈瑞\NHarry...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.50,1:44:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那枚核弹的计时器在跳\Nthe clock on that ninefoot nuclear weapon is ticking.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.42,1:44:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-我的天 -夏普，给我进来\N-Oh, my God! -Sharp! Get back here now!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:10.26,1:44:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,马上准备撤退\NWhat? Get the shuttle ready to evac now!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.59,1:44:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-核弹突然启动，这是怎么回事？ -紧急程序\NIt just came on all by itself. What the hell's happening?  Secondary protocol.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:15.31,1:44:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么？ -紧急程序\NWhat's that? What?  Secondary protocol.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.35,1:44:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么意思？ -紧急程序是什么？\NWhat does that mean?  What the hell's secondary protocol?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:19.23,1:44:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他们要从地球引爆核弹\NThey're detonating this thing from Earth.  What do you mean, detonating?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.19,1:44:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,引爆？我们都还没钻好洞\NWe haven't even drilled the hole yet!  We'll drop it in the hole.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.06,1:44:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,快戴上头盔\NWhat're you talkin' about?  The hole? Whoa, whoa!  Get your helmets on now!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:25.23,1:44:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，怎么关掉？我的手下在外面\NOh, no, no. HowHow you turn it off?  I got two men out on that rock!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.32,1:44:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我也有，我们得撤退\NI got a man out there too. We gotta evac now.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.74,1:44:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,色狼、麦斯 快回到航天飞机\NMax, Rockhound, get back to the shuttle, doubletime!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.74,1:44:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他们也许正要下来\NThey could be on their way here.  They're not on their way here.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:35.74,1:44:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是的话，早就该看到他们了\NThey would've talked to us by now. We would've seen them.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:38.58,1:44:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,封锁驾驶舱\NWatts, air lock the cockpit now!  I copy you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.79,1:44:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,麦斯、色狼 等等，怎么把它关掉？\NMax, Rockhound!  Hey, wait a minute! How do you turn this thing off?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:45.17,1:44:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,哈瑞，收到吗？出事了\N[Radio Static Hissing]  Harry, do you copy?  Somethin's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.67,1:44:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，我们根本就不该来\NYeah, it's all wrong, man. We shouldn't even be up here.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.47,1:44:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,回航天飞机吧\NI know. Let's go back to the ship!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.59,1:44:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能丢下他们\NI'm not leavin' without my men, Sharp.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.31,1:44:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,两分钟内就得离开\NWe've got two and a half minutes to drop it and get off this rock.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.60,1:45:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他们赶不回来我们就走\NIf they're not back by the time we finish, we leave without 'em.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:01.98,1:45:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,别这么复杂，把核弹关掉\NOkay, let's simplify this. Let's just turn the bomb off right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:04.48,1:45:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,要是不在八百英尺的地底下引爆核弹的话\NIf we don't put this bomb down in a hole 800 feet onto a fault line,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.40,1:45:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这只是一场昂贵的烟火秀\Nall you're gonna have is a real expensive fireworks show.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:09.69,1:45:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这好像一场噩梦\NThis is turnin' into a surrealistic nightmare here.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:12.32,1:45:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你听到吗？我是楚门\NWatsler, are you listening? It's Truman.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:14.82,1:45:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,听着，我要你切断信号,和卫星的通讯信号\NOkay, listen to me carefully. I want you to kill it. Kill the uplink.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:30.34,1:45:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-给我时间钻洞，把核弹关掉 -这不是我的决定\N-Give us the time, Sharp. Shut this bomb down now!  -It's not my call.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:34.05,1:45:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-是谁的决定？ -这命令一定是来自总统\N-Then whose call is it?  -An order to detonate can only come from the president.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.85,1:45:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他不在这儿，快把核弹关掉\NThe president's not here! You've gotta give us more time!  Let's just turn it off now.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.81,1:45:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能决定\NI'm telling you to shut this bomb down now!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.89,1:45:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你猜怎么着？\NAnd I'm telling you it's not my call!  Well, guess what.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:42.94,1:45:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我就替你决定\NI just made the call for you.  Harry!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:47.02,1:45:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,住手，你会引爆它\NDon't. You could set it off.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:50.94,1:45:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你带枪来太空干嘛？\NOh, man. What're you doin' with a gun in space?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.66,1:46:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,快点，快关掉核弹 切断连线\NCome on. Come on. We gotta stop that bomb right now. Kill the uplink.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:02.54,1:46:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-核弹会爆炸，快把它弄出航天飞机 -别乱来\N-This thing is gonna blow. We gotta get it off the ship.  -Easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:07.92,1:46:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-别动 -关掉核弹，让我们继续\N-Stand down, Sergeant.  -Shut this bomb down and let us finish our job the right way.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.38,1:46:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我得保护核弹\NI'm under orders to protect a surface detonation.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.59,1:46:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你三秒钟 否则你就得向我开枪\NI'm gonna give you three seconds to shut this bomb down, and then I'm gonna make you shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.10,1:46:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,快点\NHurry, Watsler. For Christ's sake, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.69,1:46:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,“切断”\N[Detonator Powering Down]
Dialogue: 0,1:46:25.73,1:46:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事？\NWhat happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.57,1:46:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,长官，引爆指令被取消\NSir, the override It's been overridden.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.99,1:46:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,只有几分钟，设法恢复信号，快点\NI bought us a couple of minutes, so get that radio workin', okay? Hurry, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.62,1:46:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你大老远跑来 就是为了杀死我们吗？\NBring me all the way up here just to blow me and my friends up? Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:47.88,1:46:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说\N[Gasping] Listen  Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.09,1:46:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴，上校，你别说话\NShut up, Colonel. I'm talking now.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.59,1:46:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,核弹可能会再启动\N[Sharp] It could start again. It might've been a warning.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:59.81,1:47:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你得拆除它\NThat's why you are gonna dismantle this bomb.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.35,1:47:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我们错过什么好戏？\NAll right. What'd we miss?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:09.11,1:47:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,再试一次  去吧\NDo it again.  Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.45,1:47:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,继续试\NKeep tryin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:18.95,1:47:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,请你别反抗，马上走开 请你离开\NSir, I need you to cease and desist. I need your terminal... now.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.67,1:47:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-他们又启动核弹 -又启动了\N-They're reactivating the bomb.  -Comin' back online, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:30.09,1:47:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,老天，又来了\N[Detonator Blipping]  Oh, geez. Here we go again.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:33.09,1:47:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你来这儿有什么目的？\NWhat're you doin' up here? And why did you even bother to make the trip?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:36.43,1:47:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,奉命行事、完成任务\NTo do the right thing, to see that it's done.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:46.48,1:47:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,想想你在做什么\NFor God's sakes, think about what you're doin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.98,1:47:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你为何要听十万哩外的命令\NWhy are you listenin' to someone that's 100,000 miles away?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:53.19,1:47:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,在这儿没有人能帮我们\NWe're here. Nobody down there can help us.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:57.36,1:48:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们失败人类就会灭亡\NSo if we don't get this job done, then everybody's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:01.16,1:48:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,只剩一分钟\NOne minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.54,1:48:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我钻了三十年的油井\NI've been drillin' holes in the earth for 30 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.50,1:48:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,每次都能钻到设定的深度\NAnd I have never, never missed a depth that I have aimed for.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:11.29,1:48:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这次也能，我能钻到八百英尺\NAnd by God, I am not gonna miss this one. I will make 800 feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.76,1:48:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-42秒 -不过我需要你的帮忙\NFortytwo seconds.  But I can't do it alone, Colonel. I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.39,1:48:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你要用你女儿的姓名发誓\NYou swear on your daughter's life, on my family's,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.56,1:48:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你钻得到那个深度\Nthat you can hit that mark?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:26.56,1:48:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我钻得到八百英尺 我对天发誓\NI will make 800 feet. I swear to God, I will.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:31.69,1:48:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那就拆除这枚弹头吧\NThen let's turn this bomb off.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.95,1:48:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,稳住，拆开来，线拉出来\NSteady. Take it back. That's what you'll have to do. Get 'em off backwards.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.83,1:48:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-全部吗？ -全都要\NRainbow track? Under Under one? Under Okay.  All of 'em. All of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:53.38,1:48:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-没静电吧？ -好好干\N-Okay. Are we free of static?  -Oh, do a good job. Do a good job.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.88,1:48:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,稳住\NSteady. Steady.  Good job. All right. All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:58.93,1:49:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-快，快 -红线A，剪断\NGo! Go! Go! Red wire "A." Ready? And
Dialogue: 0,1:49:02.39,1:49:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,快点…\NNow. Come on! Come on! Come on! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.97,1:49:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,负极B线\N[Breathing Heavily]  Negative "B."
Dialogue: 0,1:49:07.23,1:49:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好好干…\NReady, and now.  Do a good job. Do a good job.  Track flipped. Hots in.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.02,1:49:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,红还是蓝？\NIt better be. Go.  Red or blue?  [Beeping Faster]
Dialogue: 0,1:49:15.73,1:49:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,红\NRe
Dialogue: 0,1:49:22.28,1:49:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝\NBlue.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:26.62,1:49:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,干得好\NGood job!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:33.54,1:49:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这里真讨厌\NOh, God, it sucks up here.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:36.92,1:49:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-计时器停在三秒 -什么？\NSir, the clock has stopped at three seconds.  What?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.47,1:49:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,完全失去联络了？\NHave we lost complete radio contact?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:43.68,1:49:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我成功了，俄国卫星接收到微弱信号\NI got some magic happening. We're bouncing off Russian and French satellites.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:46.52,1:49:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,休斯顿，收到吗？\NIt may have a faint signal.  Houston? Houston, do you copy?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:51.69,1:49:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,请说，自由号\NGo ahead, Freedom.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:54.15,1:49:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,休斯顿，你有个问题\NHouston, you have a problem Problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:57.32,1:49:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我答应女儿我要回家\NSee, I promised my little girl that I'd be comin' home.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:00.07,1:50:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不管你们怎么想，我们都得钻洞\NNow, I don't know what you people are doin' down there, but we got a hole to dig up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:05.99,1:50:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊,我们接着干活\N[Cheering]  Go, go, go, go! Come on. We got work to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.50,1:50:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,很好，绝不放弃，怎么样？\NOkay, guys. All go, no quit. How ya doin' down there? Good?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:13.42,1:50:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,装好变速器，干活吧\NOkay, got the tranny. We're back in business.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:16.38,1:50:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你们应该休息一下，过来看看\NHey, you guys should take a break and come up and see this.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:21.51,1:50:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,地球好美，\NWow. Got a great view of the Earth from here.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:24.39,1:50:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,可惜回不去了\NToo bad we'll never set foot on her again.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.72,1:50:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-勒夫，看到什么了吗？ -没有\N-Lev, do you see anything?  -No.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:29.02,1:50:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,继续前进，我不会放弃\NWell, keep goin'. I'm not givin' up.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:32.19,1:50:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,停下来，大熊\NHold up here, Bear.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:34.44,1:50:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,老天\N[Lev] Oh, boy.  [A.J.] This is great.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:36.69,1:50:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了，在陨石上碰到大峡谷\NWe just happen to run into the Grand Canyon on the asteroid?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:39.69,1:50:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我就说你走错路了\NI told you, you took a wrong way, a wrong road.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:43.03,1:50:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？这地方哪儿来的路？\N[A.J.] WhatWhat road? Do you see any roads around here?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:46.37,1:50:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想扫你的兴\N[Lev] You know what? I do not have much pleasure being near God's ear.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:50.54,1:50:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不过这样好吗？\NBut you think this is looking good, or what?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:53.21,1:50:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,勒夫，拜托你给我住嘴\NLev, why don't you just do humanity a favour and just shut the hell up?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:02.13,1:51:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你看过飞车特技吗？\NHave you ever heard of Evel Knievel?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.64,1:51:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我没看过“星球大战”\NNo, I never saw Star Wars.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:13.23,1:51:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,很好，你们干得很好\NAll right. Doin' a good job.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:15.81,1:51:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-深度多少？ -150英尺\N-Give me a depth reading, Max.  -We're 150 feet, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:23.66,1:51:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,骑吧，牛仔\NRide 'em, cowboy! Yippeekaiyo, kaiyay!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:27.45,1:51:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,从核弹上面下来\NGet off... the nuclear... warhead.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:31.75,1:51:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我在学“奇爱博士”里面\NI was doin' that guy from that movie, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:33.87,1:51:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,骑着核弹的那场戏\NSlim Pickens, where he rides it all the way in the nuclear warhead.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:37.09,1:51:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-下来 -你没看过吗？\N-Now.  -Oh, you didn't see that one, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:40.01,1:51:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,还得钻700英尺，色狼\NWe got 700 feet of hole to dig, Rockhound.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:42.97,1:51:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想感受胯下的威力\NAll right. JustJust wanted to feel the power between my legs, brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:48.22,1:51:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,夏普\NHey, Sharp.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:50.64,1:51:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,反对核武！反对核武！\N[Chanting] No nukes! No nukes! No nukes!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:53.94,1:51:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你的枪还有子弹吗？\NYou got any more bullets in that gun, Sharp?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:56.15,1:51:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,华特说被踢一脚就会漂出去\N[A.J.] What did Watts tell you, Bear? If she kicked you in the balls, you'd keep floating.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:02.07,1:52:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,关掉推进器，\N[A.J.] We turn the thrusters off,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:04.07,1:52:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,让它漂过去\Nwe jump this thing, we float right over it.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:06.57,1:52:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,再说一遍\NGo over it again, Lev.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:08.79,1:52:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一离地，就关掉推进器\NThrow the jet thrusters off exactly when we jump.  Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:13.71,1:52:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,只要再启动就能降落\NAnd then we're gonna put them on, and we gonna go down nice and slow.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:16.71,1:52:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,没错，没错 能成功吗？\NThat's it. That's it, baby. That's it.  Is this gonna work?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:19.80,1:52:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-不知道 -说说谎话安慰我嘛\N-I don't know.  -Lev, you know what, just lie to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:23.97,1:52:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,也许有五成把握\NLet's say 5050 No. More like, uh
Dialogue: 0,1:52:27.22,1:52:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不，七、八成吧\Nlike 7030 or 8020.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.39,1:52:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了你们就是英雄,跟我一样\NBut you know what? If it works, the two of you gonna be heroes, just like me.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:35.48,1:52:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,管它的，跳过去吧\NScrew it. We're jumpin' over this canyon.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:42.11,1:52:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,老实说，这点子很烂\NJust for the record, this is a very bad idea!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:48.62,1:52:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,到了悬崖再关掉\NWait for the edge. Don't hit it till we get there.  I'm waiting.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:53.83,1:52:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,来了\N[Lev] Three.  [A.J. Chattering]
Dialogue: 0,1:52:56.83,1:52:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,二…一，关掉！\N[Lev] Two. One!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:08.97,1:53:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了！\NYes! It's working!  It's working!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:15.81,1:53:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我是天才 等一下\NI'm a genius! Wait a minute.  Whoa. Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:20.65,1:53:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-前面有岩石 -左转，左转\NWe got some rocks!  Go left! Go left!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:23.03,1:53:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,没办法\NLev, Lev, I can't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:34.87,1:53:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要漂到外太空了\NOh, okay, okay, we're floating into outer space.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:37.96,1:53:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个问题\NCheck main switch.  Uh, this could be a little bit of a problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:41.63,1:53:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-启动推进器 -启动\NThrusters on... now!  All right, turn 'em on.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:43.88,1:53:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？\N[Rattling]  What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:47.72,1:53:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不晓得，推进器失效 这个臭机器\NII don't know. TheThe thrusters not working. I hate this machine!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:52.26,1:53:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是计划好了？\NI thought you had this planned! What're we supposed to do?  Be quiet! I must think!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:54.81,1:53:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-让我想想，我要出去 -你要出去？\NI'm stepping outside.  You'reYou're going outside?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:57.98,1:54:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,只有我是合格的宇航员 我要救你们这些美国佬\NI am the only certified astronaut, and I'm saving your American ass!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:06.78,1:54:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,谁叫你要听他的\NYes. You'll listen to him. Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:14.91,1:54:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,快点，离地面已经有一哩了\NHurry up, Lev, because we're about a mile off the asteroid!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:18.79,1:54:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，燃料管结冰了\NJust a second. The fuel line is iced up.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:22.21,1:54:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-应该可以了 -还是不行\NI think maybe workin' now.  No, Lev, it's not working!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:26.63,1:54:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉，我算错机率了\NI'm sorry, A.J. I was way off the odds.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:29.59,1:54:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,越来越高了\N[Bear] We're gettin' higher, man.  Look out!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:32.26,1:54:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,小心，有岩石！\NThe rocks! Rocks are coming!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:41.11,1:54:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,抓紧了\NHold on!  Aah!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:46.95,1:54:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-启动推进器 -勒夫，小心\NPull the thrusters!  Lev, look out!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:56.29,1:54:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-勒夫不见了 -小杰\NWe lost Lev.  A.J.! [Grunting]
Dialogue: 0,1:54:59.37,1:55:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,小杰，推进器\NA.J., the thrusters!  Aah!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:05.88,1:55:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,推进器启动了\NLet's get Lev back!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:16.52,1:55:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,抓紧，要降落了\NLev, hold on! We're comin' in!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:35.49,1:55:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,谢天谢地，阿弥陀佛，谢谢…\NThank You, Jesus. Thank You, Lord. Thank You. Thank You, thank You, thank You, thank You.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:42.67,1:55:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-我是真正的俄国大英雄 -我就说吧\N-Now I'm really a Russian hero!  -I told you!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:48.26,1:55:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,一定能成功\NI know!  I knew this would work!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:50.84,1:55:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我算得没错\NGood odds, you know?  Come on, Lev.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:53.30,1:55:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,上来，快走吧\NGet in here. We gotta go.  Yah!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:59.35,1:56:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你要注意变速器\NRockhound, keep on that transmission.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:01.77,1:56:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题\NTranny looks good, Harry.  All right. Take it outta there.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:04.19,1:56:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好，放下去吧 锁住了\NLock it down, Chick.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:07.82,1:56:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了\NNice.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:11.53,1:56:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么没玩过这个？\NHow come we didn't get any training on this thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:14.28,1:56:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,酷毙了，我一个人就能搞定这陨石\NWhoa. Very cool. I could take out this asteroid singlehandedly.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:18.04,1:56:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,让我接手吧\N[Machine Whirring]  Okay, boys, give it a rest. I'll take it from here.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:24.50,1:56:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么？\NWhat the hell is that?  It's Rockhound.  Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:27.05,1:56:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,真好玩，太爽了\NThis is so much fun, it's freaky.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:31.18,1:56:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,色狼\NRockhound!  [Cheering]
Dialogue: 0,1:56:33.39,1:56:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,小心头，抱歉，哈瑞\NWhoa, watch your heads. Sorry, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:38.10,1:56:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,快让开\NOutta my way, boys!  Rockhound!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:40.98,1:56:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,臭陨石，去死吧\NMeet your maker, asteroid!  [Both Grunting]
Dialogue: 0,1:56:47.94,1:56:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-你是怎么了？ -太疯狂了\N-What the hell's the matter with you, Rockhound? Goddamn!  -This is insane.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:51.40,1:56:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-你疯了吗？ -他有太空妄想症\N-Have you lost your mind?  -No.  He's got space dementia.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:55.37,1:56:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,看好你的手下\NHarry, you want to watch your man.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:00.08,1:57:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,麦斯,换到倒档，把管子弄出来\NMax, downshift and put it in reverse. We gotta get that pipe outta there.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:10.09,1:57:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事？ -地面裂开来,地震\N-What's happening?  -The ground's cracking!  -Earthquake!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:21.27,1:57:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,快关掉\NQuick, shut it off!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:24.73,1:57:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,快关掉…天然气爆发\NShut it off! Shut it off now!  We're gonna have a blowout!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:28.19,1:57:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,挖到天然气层,压力太大了\NWe hit a gas pocket!  We got pressure out the ass!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:32.95,1:57:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,麦斯，快戴头盔，要爆发了\NMax, get your helmet on! Max, she's gonna blow!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:36.91,1:57:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-老天，好烫 -快走吧\NAah! Oh, Jesus, I'm cooking!  Max, get outta there!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:40.12,1:57:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,完了,哈瑞！\NThis is it! Harry!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:46.59,1:57:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我快被烫死了\NI'm bailing!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:51.76,1:57:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,麦斯\NMax!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:55.26,1:57:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,永别了，麦斯\NGoodbye, Max.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:57.47,1:58:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,安息吧，伙计\NMax!  Take care, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:00.89,1:58:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,穿山甲不见了,天然气爆发\NArmadillo's off the scope.  I think we've had a blowout.  No sign of the Armadillo.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:35.97,1:58:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,通知楚门\NGet ahold of Truman.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:39.35,1:58:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,让世界知道噩耗\NPrepare the world for bad news.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:48.61,1:58:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,根据未经证实的消息\N[Male Newscaster #1] We're getting sketchy information that the mission...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:51.48,1:58:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,太空任务遭遇重大挫折\Nhas suffered massive failure.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:54.20,1:58:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正在\NAnd what we're trying to do right now...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:56.20,1:58:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,打听确切的消息\Nis to confirm that and find out exactly what that means.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:58.37,1:59:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,据赶回家和家人团聚的\NRepeat: We're getting leaks from several NASA officials,
Dialogue: 0,1:59:01.37,1:59:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,太空总署官员透露\Nsome rushing home to be with their families,
Dialogue: 0,1:59:03.91,1:59:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,钻洞行动不成功\Nthat the drilling was unsuccessful.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:15.84,1:59:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这是人类灭亡的前夕\N[Male Newscaster #2] This could very well be our final hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:22.52,1:59:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要结束转播\N[Male Newscaster #4] We're gonna go off the air now.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:24.52,1:59:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,祝好运，上帝保佑大家\NGood luck and God bless.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:31.02,1:59:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,有陨石掉落\N[Man #1] We've got incoming.  [Man #2] I got tracks.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:32.90,1:59:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,欧洲一共有四颗，\NNORAD's tracking four small incoming over Europe.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:35.07,1:59:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,一颗就快要击中巴黎\NI think one's about to hit near Paris.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:00.85,2:00:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,根据报导…\N[All Shouting]  Reports are coming in.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:04.85,2:00:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,42国实施戒严令\N[Male Newscaster #1] Martial law has been implemented in 42 countries.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:07.77,2:00:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,当陨石突破最后屏障\N[Male Newscaster #2] Once the asteroid hits zero barrier,
Dialogue: 0,2:00:10.11,2:00:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,3小时57分后将撞上地球\Nit will take about three hours and 57 minutes to impact Earth.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:18.24,2:00:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得奉总统命令叫他们撤离\NI guess we do it the president's way.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:20.24,2:00:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,然后摇控引爆核弹\NI'll order an evac. You can remote detonate.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:22.53,2:00:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-你还是认为无效？ -已经无所谓了\NYou still don't think this'll work, do you?  What I think is irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:25.79,2:00:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们必须马上引爆 -好吧\N[Kimsey] We need to do it now.  -Fine.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:28.83,2:00:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-他们能起飞吗？ -希望能\N-Can they still take off?  -We hope so.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:31.04,2:00:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,都是你害的\NYou are the one that pulled them into this!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:33.21,2:00:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是我的家人,别说你希望能\NThat is my family up there, so I don't wanna hear, "We hope so"!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:42.26,2:00:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,猜怎么着？面对死亡吧\NGuess what, guys? It's time to embrace the horror.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:45.60,2:00:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能亲眼目睹地球灭亡\NLook. We got frontrow tickets to the end of the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:11.46,2:01:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,耶 干得好\NYeah!  Way to go, baby!  Harry!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:22.43,2:01:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,哈瑞，怎么样？\NYo, Harry! What's up, baby?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:25.35,2:01:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,把核弹抬走，钻洞吧\NHey, get that bomb outta there! We got a hole to make!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:28.39,2:01:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,休斯顿，难以置信，\N[Sharp] Houston, you're not gonna believe this,
Dialogue: 0,2:01:32.02,2:01:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,另一架穿山甲到了\Nbut the other Armadillo has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:34.69,2:01:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,大伙听着，冷静下来\N[Cheering, Applauding]  All right, people, listen up. Settle down and focus.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:38.19,2:01:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你男朋友回来了\NMechanical, get online.  P.P.O., gimme a setup.  Your boyfriend's back.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:43.16,2:01:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,哈瑞，来吧\N[Bear] Yo, Harry!  [Shouting]
Dialogue: 0,2:01:45.70,2:01:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,哈瑞，想我吗？\NHey, Harry. You miss me?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:48.96,2:01:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,小杰，我只想说五个字\NA.J., I got just five words for ya.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:52.63,2:01:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-能见到你真好 -那是六个字\N-Damn glad to see ya, boy!  -That's six words.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:56.05,2:01:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-带他们去吧 -洞在哪里？\NChick, walk 'em down.  [A.J.] So where's this hole you need dug?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:59.17,2:02:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,重新开始钻洞\N[Watts] Houston, drilling has recommenced.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:02.05,2:02:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,一小时内能钻250英尺吗？\NDo you think they can drill 250 feet in an hour?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:05.64,2:02:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,最好能\NThey better.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:07.72,2:02:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,固定好\NBring that piece on in, Bear.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:10.48,2:02:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,最高动力\NTractor pull.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:13.23,2:02:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,钻臂降下 还有250英尺\NI'm comin' down!  We got 250 feet to go.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:16.65,2:02:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这是 最后一具变速器和钻头\NIt's our last transmission, last drill head.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:19.82,2:02:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,一档，钻吧，下去了\NPunch it through. First gear. We got contact.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:23.91,2:02:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-钻进去吧，小杰 -我来了，钻吧\NCome on down, A.J.  [Grunting] I got this, man. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:28.95,2:02:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,检查右引擎 飞行前检查没反应\NLev, the right engine hub. Houston, I'm getting no response from the preflight sequence.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:33.00,2:02:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不公平，拜托帮我松绑\N[Muffled] Come on, now. This is not Hey Hey, come here.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:44.14,2:02:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,勒夫，右引擎\N[Watts] Lev, the right engine  Okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:46.68,2:02:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想在临死前及时行乐\NLemme outta here, will ya? Just tryin' to have some fun before I die!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:49.77,2:02:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-有多深？ -770英尺\N-How deep are we?  -Seven seventy.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:58.69,2:03:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-又有问题 -又有活动\N-Whoa, they got problems.  -The gauges are spiking.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:00.90,2:03:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,关掉，退出来\NMethane! Shut it down! Back it down!
Dialogue: 0,2:03:03.07,2:03:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不能退，没时间了\NI can't pull back now. The bit'll get lodged. We don't have enough time!
Dialogue: 0,2:03:07.20,2:03:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,会爆掉的,麦斯就是这样死的\NWhoa, whoa, whoa! It's gonna blow! It's how we lost Max!
Dialogue: 0,2:03:11.08,2:03:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我，钻得过去的，没问题\NI know what I'm talkin' about. We can punch through this. We can knock this outta the park.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:14.96,2:03:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,只剩这架变速器\NThis is our last transmission, A.J.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:16.88,2:03:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,该死，若是只能相信我一次\NGoddamn it, if you're ever gonna trust me, ever,
Dialogue: 0,2:03:19.13,2:03:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是现在了\Nonce in your life, trust me now!
Dialogue: 0,2:03:22.01,2:03:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-会爆的 -我能办到，你要相信我\N-Harry, it's gonna blow!  -Harry, I know what I'm doin'. You just gotta trust me.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:27.76,2:03:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,由你决定\NMake the call.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:31.64,2:03:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我要继续钻\NAll right. Hold on. I'm pushin' through her.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:40.74,2:03:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,钻过去了\NI'm pushin' through her!
Dialogue: 0,2:03:42.95,2:03:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-深度多少？ -775英尺、780英尺\N-What's your depth?  -Seven seventyfive. Seven eighty.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:46.62,2:03:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,钻到姥姥家吧\NTake it up, baby! Ram it home!
Dialogue: 0,2:03:49.45,2:03:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,钻下去，小杰\N[Grunts] Drive on down, A.J.!
Dialogue: 0,2:03:51.62,2:03:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,785英尺，加油\NSeven eightyfive. Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:54.33,2:03:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,加油，小杰\NCome on, A.J.!  Punch it!  Ninetyone. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:57.50,2:04:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,792英尺、795英尺\NSeven ninetytwo. Seven ninetyfive!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:00.76,2:04:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,钻呀\NDrive it down, A.J.!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:03.47,2:04:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,797英尺、799英尺\NSeven ninetyseven! Ninetynine!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:06.05,2:04:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,钻过去了,802英尺，成功了\NBreakthrough!  Eight hundred! Eightohtwo, Harry!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:09.43,2:04:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了\NYeah!  We did it!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:11.48,2:04:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了\N[All Cheering]  Yes!  We did it!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:14.94,2:04:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,干得好\NYeah! Kid, way to go!  I knew it, baby!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:19.15,2:04:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他们得把核弹放进洞里,只剩下38分钟\NIt's not over till we get the bomb down that hole.  Watts, they've got 38 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:43.38,2:04:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,哈瑞，你得让开\N[Sharp] Harry, you've gotta give me that hole.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:45.38,2:04:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,等我两分钟，管子卡住了\NI'm gonna need two more minutes. I got a bent pipe jammed in the hole.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:49.14,2:04:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得把它取出来\NWe gotta cut it out before we can send that bomb down. A.J.!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:51.89,2:04:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-小杰，准备好了？ -准备好了\NShe good to go?  Yeah, I'm all set.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:54.39,2:04:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:01.44,2:05:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你要快点\NAll right.  [Harry] A.J., come on! Make it fast!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:04.07,2:05:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我会尽快，下面的气压很高\NI'm goin' as fast as I can! There's a lot of gas pressure!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:12.87,2:05:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉到吗？\NYou feel that?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:14.87,2:05:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,哈瑞，快点，核弹准备好了\NHarry, you gotta give me that hole. The bomb is almost ready.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:17.75,2:05:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,快好了，\N[Harry] Pull that pipe out!  Harry, I'm almost through!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:20.29,2:05:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,再给我15秒\NGive me 15 more seconds!  [Rumbling]
Dialogue: 0,2:05:27.18,2:05:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这倒是没见过\NWell, this is somethin' new.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:29.93,2:05:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这颗陨石讨厌我们\N[Crashing]  I don't think this thing likes us.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:33.10,2:05:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我们要毁了它\NThat's 'cause it knows we're here to kill it.  Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:41.36,2:05:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,上面怎么了？\NHey, what's goin' on up there?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:47.82,2:05:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-小杰 -搞什么？\NA.J.!  What the hell was that?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:51.91,2:05:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我好了\NA.J.!  Goddamn it, I'm finished!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:56.62,2:05:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-你没事吧？ -气压很高\N-A.J., you all right?  -Oh, lot of gas pressure in here, man!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:59.33,2:06:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-拉我上去 -是氢气\N-Get me out!  -Whoa, whoa, whoa! Hydrogen pocket!
Dialogue: 0,2:06:19.02,2:06:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,救命啊！\NOh! Harry! Pull me in!
Dialogue: 0,2:06:24.11,2:06:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,小杰，撑着点\N[Grunting]  Aah! A.J., hang on!
Dialogue: 0,2:06:34.20,2:06:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,保护核弹\NSecure the bomb!
Dialogue: 0,2:06:37.00,2:06:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,夏普，小心\NSharp, heads up!
Dialogue: 0,2:06:39.83,2:06:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,古柏，快跑\NGruber! Get outta there now!
Dialogue: 0,2:06:51.93,2:06:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,快跑\N[Whimpering] Oh, God, no!
Dialogue: 0,2:07:16.75,2:07:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你相信吗？\NDo you believe that just happened?  [Gas Hissing]
Dialogue: 0,2:07:22.00,2:07:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,-夏普，你没事吧？ -我没事\N-Sharp, you all right?  -I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:24.75,2:07:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-大熊？ -没事，我在这儿\N-Bear?  -Yeah. I'm here, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:27.05,2:07:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-小杰 -我没事\N-A.J.?  -Yeah, I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:29.63,2:07:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们失去古柏\N[Gas Hissing]  We lost Gruber.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:34.72,2:07:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,古柏死了\NGruber's dead.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:37.06,2:07:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,把核弹装好回家吧\NLet's get that bomb ready and go home.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:47.53,2:07:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕了 “错误”\N[Sharp] Oh, my God.  [Beeping]
Dialogue: 0,2:07:49.99,2:07:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-有问题吗？ -计时器和摇控器坏了\NIs there a problem, Colonel?  The timer, the remote, the whole thing's dead.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:54.37,2:07:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,核弹坏了？\NWhat, the bomb is dead?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:56.54,2:08:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,遥控引爆器一定是刚才被石块打坏了\NNo, the trigger's dead. It must've gotten damaged during the rock storm.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:02.21,2:08:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那该怎么引爆？\NSo how do we detonate it?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:14.39,2:08:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-再过18分钟就突破最后屏障 -有坏消息\NWe have 18 minutes to zero barrier. We got some bad news.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:19.27,2:08:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,摇控引爆器受到损坏\NThe remote detonator on the bomb has been damaged.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:23.10,2:08:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,有人得留下来引爆\NThat means that somebody's gonna have to stay behind.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:28.57,2:08:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,航天飞机要两个人驾驶\NIt takes two people to fly this thing.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:30.95,2:08:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不想留下来等死的话 你们就得抽签决定\NEither we all stay and die, or you guys draw straws.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:35.20,2:08:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我说咱们留下来等死,这是我的想法\NI say we all stay and die. But that's me.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:39.79,2:08:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿意抽签，抽签吧\NI'll draw. Let's draw.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:44.42,2:08:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不必抽签\NNobody's gonna draw straws.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:47.92,2:08:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-我留下来引爆 -不行\NI'll stay and take care of it.  Well, I can't live with that sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:50.59,2:08:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,没人问你\NNobody asked you if you could live with it, all right?  Bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,2:08:52.80,2:08:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能让你自愿牺牲\NNo way I will let you volunteer for this...
Dialogue: 0,2:08:55.51,2:08:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,然后良心不安地回家\Nso I can go back to my home country like the man who didn't volunteer.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:59.31,2:09:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不行\NNo way!
Dialogue: 0,2:09:01.31,2:09:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们抽签决定谁留下来\NHey, man, let's draw, and let's see who's gonna stay up here and dance.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:06.11,2:09:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你们一定觉得我疯了\NGuys, lll know you guys think I'm crazy right now,
Dialogue: 0,2:09:08.61,2:09:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我想留下来\Nbut I would really like this responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:11.53,2:09:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NAll right. All right.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:14.07,2:09:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-我能搞定 -那就抽吧\NI can do it.  Let's just draw straws and get it over with. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:18.20,2:09:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不跟你抽签\NI ain't drawin' against you, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:19.95,2:09:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我要跟你抽签，快抽吧\NWell, I'm gonna draw against you, Chick, so you better just go ahead and do it.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:24.08,2:09:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,给我吧\NJust gimme this thing.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:33.09,2:09:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这算好还是不好？\NIs this good or bad?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:40.77,2:09:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,老天\NOh, man.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:43.69,2:09:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,人难逃一死，对吧？\NWell, we all gotta die, right?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:50.65,2:09:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,至少我能拯救世界\NI'm the guy who gets to do it saving the world.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:53.03,2:09:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,快点，只剩十分钟\NSo, uh, let's go. WeWe got about ten minutes, right?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:58.99,2:10:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,把这个插进插座\NYou plug this into the port.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:01.04,2:10:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,拉起来然后按住 就这样\NLift, press, hold. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:06.38,2:10:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,拉起来按住，应该不难,连我都不会搞砸\NLift, press, hold. Shouldn't be too tough. Even I can't screw this up.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:09.88,2:10:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我带他下去\NI'll take him down.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:46.46,2:10:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我个忙\NDo me a favour, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:49.25,2:10:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉葛瑞丝\NJust tell Grace that, uh
Dialogue: 0,2:10:52.51,2:10:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我会永远和她在一起，好吗？\Nthat I'll always be with her, okay?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:57.43,2:10:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好不好？\NCan you do that?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:00.93,2:11:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，小子\NYeah. Okay, kid.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:09.11,2:11:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,把这交给楚门\NGive this to Truman.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:11.28,2:11:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要给他,进去吧\NMake sure Truman gets that. Get in there.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:20.41,2:11:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,轮到我表现了\NIt's my turn now.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:22.66,2:11:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,哈瑞\N[Gasping] Harry! Harry!
Dialogue: 0,2:11:25.71,2:11:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能这样,这是我的使命\NYou can't do this to me! It's my job!
Dialogue: 0,2:11:31.00,2:11:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你要照雇我女儿 那才是你的使命\NYou go take care of my little girl now. That's your job.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:39.18,2:11:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我一直都把你当儿子\NAlways thought of you as a son.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:41.39,2:11:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,一直都是\NAlways.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:43.43,2:11:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你和葛瑞丝结婚我会很高兴\NBut I'd be damn proud to have you marry Grace.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:47.19,2:11:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你要保重\NHarry.  You take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:50.98,2:11:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你，孩子\NHarry, no!  I love you, pal.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:53.11,2:11:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我也爱你，等等，哈瑞\NHarry, I love you! Don't, Harry! Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,2:11:56.11,2:11:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,永别了\NMy son.  Don't do this, Harry!
Dialogue: 0,2:11:58.74,2:12:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样，哈瑞…\NDon't do this! Harry!
Dialogue: 0,2:12:09.67,2:12:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事？\NWhat happened?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:12.75,2:12:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那个固执的疯子\NThat crazy, stubborn son of a
Dialogue: 0,2:12:20.97,2:12:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这真是个好点子\NWell, this was a real good idea.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:23.97,2:12:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,快点，夏普 快把他们带走\NAll right, let's go, Sharp. Let's get our team outta here.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:33.07,2:12:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,准备启动推进器\NCome on! Let's get ready to initiate thrusters! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,2:12:38.11,2:12:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,坐好了\NStrap it in, guys!  Get the O2 masks.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:40.82,2:12:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,检查燃料，可以了吗？\NAre they green? Are they green?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:44.16,2:12:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我不敢相信… 你没事吧？\NI can't believe this is going down like this. You all right?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:47.75,2:12:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,关闭通风孔、输入燃料 引擎没有问题\NO2 vents locked, pressure loaded.  Engine board is green.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:56.05,2:12:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,休斯顿，收到吗？ 我是哈瑞·史坦普\NHouston, do you copy? This is Harry Stamper.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:07.68,2:13:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要在三分钟后离开\N[Man] Houston, we're outta here in T minus three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:12.44,2:13:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸？\NDaddy! [Chuckling]
Dialogue: 0,2:13:15.65,2:13:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,葛瑞丝\NHi, Gracie. Hi, honey.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:18.57,2:13:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,乖女儿,我知道我答应你要回去\NGrace, I know I promised you I was comin' home.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:23.62,2:13:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白\NI don't under understand.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:25.62,2:13:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,看来我得食言了\N[Sighs] Looks like I'm gonna have to break that promise.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:32.54,2:13:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我也骗了你\NI, um I lied to you, too,
Dialogue: 0,2:13:36.26,2:13:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我说我跟你不同\Nwhen I told you that I didn't want to be like you.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:41.43,2:13:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我跟你一样\NBecause I am like you.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:43.55,2:13:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我有什么优点 这都是来自你\NAnd everything good that I have inside of me, I have from you.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:49.31,2:13:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我好爱你\NI love you so much, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:52.06,2:13:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我以你为荣\NI'm so proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:54.11,2:13:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我好怕\NI'm so scared.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:56.65,2:13:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我好害怕\NI'm so scared.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:59.49,2:14:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道，很快你就不必害怕了\NI know it, baby, but there won't be anything to be scared of soon.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:07.16,2:14:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你知道，小杰救了我们,是真的\NGracie, I want you to know that A.J. saved us. He did.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:14.00,2:14:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,跟奇克说...\NI want you to tell Chick...
Dialogue: 0,2:14:16.13,2:14:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,没有他我就办不到\Nthat I couldn't have done it without him, none of it.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:21.63,2:14:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好好照雇小杰\NI want you to take care of A.J.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:28.56,2:14:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我真希望能陪你走上红地毯\NI wish I could be there to walk you down the aisle.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:34.65,2:14:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不过…\NBut I'll
Dialogue: 0,2:14:38.49,2:14:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我会时常去看你的\N[Sighs] I'll look in on you from time to time, okay, honey?
Dialogue: 0,2:14:44.41,2:14:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你，葛瑞丝\NI love you, Grace.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:46.41,2:14:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我也爱你\N[Crying] I love you too.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:48.20,2:14:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-我得走了 -爸爸，别走\N-I gotta go now, honey.  -Daddy, no.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:51.08,2:14:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸，不…\NNo, no, Dad, no.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:02.22,2:15:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,启动导航系统，输入燃料\N[Watts] O.M.S. pod prestart. O2 vents locked, pressure loaded.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:07.35,2:15:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事？你们怎么还不走？\NWhat the hell's goin' on up there? Why haven't you guys left yet?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:09.56,2:15:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要走了，休斯顿\NWe're going, Harry. Houston.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:12.44,2:15:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-启动导航系统 -确认\NWe got O.M.S. pod prestart.  Pod prestart confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:17.40,2:15:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？不知道\NWhat's the problem?  I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:19.61,2:15:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,快去修好\NWhat's wrong?  Fix it now!
Dialogue: 0,2:15:23.20,2:15:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,来不及了\NNo time, no time!
Dialogue: 0,2:15:25.37,2:15:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事？\NWhat?  What's that?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:31.16,2:15:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你上哪儿？\NWhere you goin'?  Come on. We're stayin', we're goin'.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:33.42,2:15:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,到底要不要走嘛？赶快决定吧\NWe're stayin', we're goin'. Make up your minds.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:35.42,2:15:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,快走吧，不到三分钟了\NSharp, get out of here now. You got less than three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:42.76,2:15:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,快呀，华特\NCome on, Watts. Come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:44.22,2:15:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,引爆吧，我们与你同在\NBlow the bomb, Harry. We're with you.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:46.14,2:15:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-卡住了 -退后，你不懂这些设备\N-Uh, it's stuck. -Yes?  You don't know the components!
Dialogue: 0,2:15:50.39,2:15:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,美国设备、俄国设备,全都是台湾制造\NComponents, American components, Russian components. All made in Taiwan!
Dialogue: 0,2:15:55.44,2:15:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,时间不多了\NWe're gettin' tight for ignition, Freedom.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:00.32,2:16:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,休斯顿，引擎点不着\NHouston, we've got no fire.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:02.61,2:16:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么意思？ -航天飞机坏了\N-What does that mean?  -It means we got a busted ship.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:04.57,2:16:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,航天飞机坏了？我却被绑在这儿\NA busted ship? And I'm strapped in here.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:07.16,2:16:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我本来在外面有好座位的\NI had a great spot picked out there.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:09.37,2:16:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,快启动引擎，来不及了\NFreedom, you fire that engine. If there's not a way, you find a way. The clock's tickin'.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:12.96,2:16:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,快启动引擎\NLet's go! Let's fire that engine, Freedom!
Dialogue: 0,2:16:14.79,2:16:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,只剩一分钟 别以为我不会引爆\NYou got less than a minute. Don't think I won't blow this thing.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:19.80,2:16:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,快走，情况不妙\NSharp, get out of here. It's gettin' bad down here.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:23.30,2:16:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,让我来修理\NI know how to fix it. Please, move.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:25.51,2:16:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你不滚开我就不客气\NII have to take you away if you don't move.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:28.43,2:16:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,快启动引擎\NWatts, you gotta get that shuttle started. You gotta fire it up now!
Dialogue: 0,2:16:30.81,2:16:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,夏普，快起飞\NDamn it, Sharp. Get off this rock!
Dialogue: 0,2:16:33.10,2:16:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫你让开\NI'm telling you, please, move! This is how we fix problem...
Dialogue: 0,2:16:36.69,2:16:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我都是这么修理俄国空间站的\Nin the Russian space station.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:39.94,2:16:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想再留在这里了\NBecause I don't want to stay here any more.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:43.61,2:16:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,终于能回家了\N[Whirring]  Yeah! Finally! We can go home!
Dialogue: 0,2:16:49.41,2:16:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,终于好了…可以了\NShe's coming back. She's coming back.  We're hot!
Dialogue: 0,2:16:51.83,2:16:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,快点，快点\NWatts! Let's go, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,2:16:54.25,2:16:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管闹吧，臭石头\NRain all you want, you son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:58.08,2:17:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,快，来不及了\NLet's go! We don't have time! Hurry, hurry. We got no time!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:01.30,2:17:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,准备启动推进器，\NInitiate thrusters on my mark!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:03.47,2:17:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,二、一…\NTwo, one, mark!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:13.31,2:17:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,快升空，快点…\NCome on. Get some altitude. Let's go, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:18.36,2:17:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,最大动力\NFreedom has max thrust!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:26.91,2:17:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你，哈瑞\NThank you, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:39.92,2:17:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,航天飞机飞远了 还没有引爆核弹\NShuttle's out of range. Still no detonation.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:46.63,2:17:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,事情不对劲\NSomething's not right. Too much time has gone by.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:51.31,2:17:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,一分钟后突破最后屏障\NZero barrier's about to be breached. One minute.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:53.72,2:17:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,快按下按钮\NHarry, come on. Press that button.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:56.44,2:18:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们回去引爆 -不，再等一分钟\NWe're goin' back and do it ourselves.  Just don't. Wait one minute.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:05.03,2:18:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-就快突破最后屏障 -哈瑞，快按钮\NDan, we're about to cross the threshold.  Come on. Press the button.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:07.99,2:18:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,上校，请你再等一分钟\NColonel, I'm askin' you. Just one more minute!
Dialogue: 0,2:18:19.08,2:18:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,快按呀\NPress the button, Stamper.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:28.59,2:18:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,哈瑞一定办得到的\NHarry'll do it. I know it.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:30.97,2:18:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他绝不会失败\NHe doesn't know how to fail.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:41.23,2:18:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们赢了，葛瑞丝\NWe win, Gracie!
Dialogue: 0,2:18:44.65,2:18:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,快按吧\NPress it!  [Beeping]
Dialogue: 0,2:19:18.69,2:19:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,引爆成功，引爆成功\N[Man On P.A.] We have detonation. Confirming detonation.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:38.79,2:19:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,陨石错过地球约四百哩\NThe two halves are gonna miss us by 400 miles...
Dialogue: 0,2:19:42.17,2:19:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,碎片大部分都被气化\Nand most of the small particles have been vaporized.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:55.89,2:19:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-休斯顿，我们回来了 -收到，自由号\N-Houston, we're comin' home.  -We copy that, Freedom.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:58.93,2:20:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,哈瑞，你是最棒的\NYo, Harry, you the man.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:55.45,2:20:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,肯尼迪中心，我看到跑道了,真是太美了\NKennedy, we see you. And you never looked so good.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:59.62,2:21:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我没提过，我最恨飞行\NI never told anybody this before but I hate flyin',
Dialogue: 0,2:21:03.37,2:21:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,所以现在摔死就太冤枉\Nso it'd be an awful shame to die now.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:05.34,2:21:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你这还不算惨,我跟高利贷借了十万块\NThat's easy for you to say. I owe 100 grand to a badass loan shark...
Dialogue: 0,2:21:09.67,2:21:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,全都花在脱衣舞娘身上\Nwhich I spent on a stripper named Molly Mounds.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:12.38,2:21:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？真糟糕\NBoy, that's bad.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:13.93,2:21:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,肯尼迪中心，副翼完全放下\NKennedy, we are 100 percent. Flap suspension control on full.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:30.82,2:21:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回家，宇航员\N[Man] Welcome home, astronauts.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:41.12,2:21:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们是大英雄\NHey, guys, remember: We're heroes now.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:43.42,2:21:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟们，别把我在上面\NSo that incident with me and the gun on the asteroid,
Dialogue: 0,2:21:45.92,2:21:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,发疯的事说出来，好吗？\Nlet's keep that under wraps, all right?
Dialogue: 0,2:22:52.61,2:22:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,史坦普小姐\NMiss Stamper.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:55.95,2:22:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我是美国空军上校夏普\NColonel Willie Sharp, United States Air Force, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:58.45,2:23:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,令尊是我见过最勇敢的人\NRequesting permission to shake the hand of the daughter...
Dialogue: 0,2:23:02.45,2:23:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,请允许我和你握手\Nof the bravest man I've ever met.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:13.09,2:23:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天,我的英雄\NOh, my God!  Hi, you're my hero.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:15.76,2:23:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,宝贝，我想跟你生个孩子\NOh, baby, I wanna have babies with you.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:21.35,2:23:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来，牛仔\NWelcome back, cowboy.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:25.23,2:23:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,哈瑞要你收下这个\NUh, Harry wanted you to have this.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:35.28,2:23:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是么…\NHe did, huh?
Dialogue: 0,2:23:55.34,2:23:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,* I could stay awake *
Dialogue: 0,2:23:57.84,2:24:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,* Just to hear you breathin' *
Dialogue: 0,2:24:03.18,2:24:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,* Watch you smile while you are sleepin' *
Dialogue: 0,2:24:07.06,2:24:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,* While you're far away and dreamin' *
Dialogue: 0,2:24:11.61,2:24:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,* I just wanna stay with you *
Dialogue: 0,2:24:15.74,2:24:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,* In this moment forever *
Dialogue: 0,2:24:18.57,2:24:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,* Forever and ever *
Dialogue: 0,2:24:21.53,2:24:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,* I don't wanna close my eyes *
Dialogue: 0,2:24:25.33,2:24:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,* I don't wanna fall asleep *
Dialogue: 0,2:24:28.00,2:24:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,* 'Cause I miss you, baby *
Dialogue: 0,2:24:30.08,2:24:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,* And I don't wanna miss a thing *
Dialogue: 0,2:24:33.30,2:24:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,* 'Cause even when I dream of you *
Dialogue: 0,2:24:37.38,2:24:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,* The sweetest dream would never do *
Dialogue: 0,2:24:40.14,2:24:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,* I'd still miss you, baby *
Dialogue: 0,2:24:42.14,2:24:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,* And I don't wanna miss a thing *
Dialogue: 0,2:24:45.81,2:24:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,* And I don't wanna miss one smile *
Dialogue: 0,2:24:49.27,2:24:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,* And I don't wanna miss one kiss *
Dialogue: 0,2:24:53.40,2:24:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,* Well, I just wanna be with you right here *
Dialogue: 0,2:24:56.82,2:25:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,* With you just like this *
Dialogue: 0,2:25:00.95,2:25:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,* Well, I just wanna hold you close *
Dialogue: 0,2:25:05.29,2:25:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,* Feel your heart so close to mine *
Dialogue: 0,2:25:09.62,2:25:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,* And just stay here in this moment *
Dialogue: 0,2:25:13.25,2:25:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,* For all the rest of time *
Dialogue: 0,2:25:17.97,2:25:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,* Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah *
Dialogue: 0,2:25:20.30,2:25:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,* Yeah *
Dialogue: 0,2:25:23.30,2:25:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,* Don't wanna close my eyes *
Dialogue: 0,2:25:27.02,2:25:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,* I don't wanna fall asleep *
Dialogue: 0,2:25:29.56,2:25:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,* 'Cause I miss you, baby *
Dialogue: 0,2:25:31.69,2:25:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,* And I don't wanna miss a thing *
Dialogue: 0,2:25:34.86,2:25:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,* 'Cause even when I dream of you *
Dialogue: 0,2:25:38.82,2:25:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,* The sweetest dream would never do *
Dialogue: 0,2:25:41.45,2:25:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,* I'd still miss you, baby *
Dialogue: 0,2:25:43.62,2:25:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,* And I don't wanna miss a thing *
Dialogue: 0,2:25:46.91,2:25:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,* Don't wanna close my eyes *
Dialogue: 0,2:25:50.12,2:25:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,* I don't wanna fall asleep *
Dialogue: 0,2:25:54.50,2:25:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,* Yeah I don't wanna miss a thing **
Dialogue: 0,2:28:55.35,2:28:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,** [Woman Vocalizing]
Dialogue: 0,2:29:03.40,2:29:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,* All my bags are packed I'm ready to go *
Dialogue: 0,2:29:08.37,2:29:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,* I'm standin' here outside your door *
Dialogue: 0,2:29:12.33,2:29:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,* I hate to wake you up to say goodbye *
Dialogue: 0,2:29:19.21,2:29:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,* But the dawn is breakin' It's early morn *
Dialogue: 0,2:29:23.67,2:29:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,* The taxi's waitin' He's blowin' his horn *
Dialogue: 0,2:29:27.43,2:29:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,* Already I'm ready I'm so lonesome *
Dialogue: 0,2:29:30.89,2:29:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,* I could die *
Dialogue: 0,2:29:34.77,2:29:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,* So kiss me and smile for me *
Dialogue: 0,2:29:39.40,2:29:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,* Tell me that you'll wait for me *
Dialogue: 0,2:29:43.19,2:29:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,* Hold me like you'll never let me go *
Dialogue: 0,2:29:49.95,2:29:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,* 'Cause I'm leaving on a jet plane *
Dialogue: 0,2:29:54.83,2:29:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,* I don't know when I'll be back again *
Dialogue: 0,2:29:59.29,2:30:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,* Oh, babe I hate to go *
Dialogue: 0,2:30:05.30,2:30:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,* I'm leaving on a jet plane *
